DofxZ68u2Z4YFUHUHd83UXLXEP74','报KET还是PET？开学前这张表帮你5分钟定下来','Cathy','每年3月开学季，我后台收到最多的一个问题就是：「Cathy，我家孩子该报KET还是PET？」    其实答案并不难，抓住3个维度，5分钟就能定下来。   01 · 先看年级和词汇量    ? 粉丝福利   关注公众号，回复「选级别」，获取K','<section style=\"font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\'PingFang SC\',\'Microsoft YaHei\',sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:16px;line-height:1.9\">\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px\">\n每年3月开学季，我后台收到最多的一个问题就是：<strong style=\"color:#2563eb\">「Cathy，我家孩子该报KET还是PET？」</strong>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px\">\n其实答案并不难，抓住3个维度，5分钟就能定下来。\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;padding:2px 0 2px 12px;margin:0 0 20px;line-height:1.4\">01 · 先看年级和词汇量</h2>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「选级别」</strong>，获取KET/PET/FCE备考全攻略 PDF！</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section style=\"background:#eff6ff;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 22px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1d4ed8\">? KET（剑桥英语A2级）</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#1e3a5f;line-height:1.85\">适合：小学5年级 ~ 初一 &nbsp;｜&nbsp; 词汇量参考：600–1200词<br>能看懂英文菜单、简短指示牌，语法以简单句为主</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff7ed;border-left:4px solid #f97316;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 28px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#c2410c\">? PET（剑桥英语B1级）</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#7c2d12;line-height:1.85\">适合：初一 ~ 初三 &nbsp;｜&nbsp; 词汇量参考：1500–2500词<br>能读英文原著故事书，能看原版动画不频繁查词</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;padding:2px 0 2px 12px;margin:0 0 20px;line-height:1.4\">02 · 一张表对照清楚</h2>\n\n<section style=\"border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:0 0 28px\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:14px\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr style=\"background:#2563eb;color:#fff\">\n      <th style=\"padding:11px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600\">对比维度</th>\n      <th style=\"padding:11px 14px;text-align:center;font-weight:600\">KET</th>\n      <th style=\"padding:11px 14px;text-align:center;font-weight:600\">PET</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;color:#475569\">适合年级</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">小5 ~ 初一</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">初一 ~ 初三</td></tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#f8fafc\"><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;color:#475569\">词汇量</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">600–1200</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">1500–2500</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;color:#475569\">备考周期</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">3–4个月</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">4–6个月</td></tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#f8fafc\"><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;color:#475569\">四项分布</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">读写各25%</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;text-align:center;color:#1a1a1a\">写作占比更大</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;color:#475569\">证书含金量</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;text-align:center;color:#f59e0b\">★★★☆☆</td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;text-align:center;color:#2563eb\">★★★★★</td></tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;border-left:4px solid #dc2626;padding:2px 0 2px 12px;margin:0 0 20px;line-height:1.4\">03 · 家长最常踩的坑</h2>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px\">\n很多家长看孩子英语成绩不错，直接跳过KET报PET——<strong style=\"color:#dc2626\">结果作文扣分严重，一次没过，孩子信心受挫。</strong>\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fecaca;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 28px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626\">⚠️ 报考前做这两步检验</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d;line-height:1.85\">① 找一套对应级别真题 → 孩子在无辅助状态下能完成70%以上，再报</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d;line-height:1.85\">② PET写作部分单独测试 → 能写出逻辑完整的80词短文，再考虑冲PET</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;color:#475569;font-size:15px\">\n不确定的话，评论区告诉我孩子年级和词汇量，我帮你判断。\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"padding:20px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#7c3aed);border-radius:14px;text-align:center\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:15px;color:#fff;font-weight:600\">? 今日练习已同步到小程序</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);line-height:1.75\">微信搜索【英语陪跑Go】→ 进入打卡 → 完成今日任务<br>坚持21天，备考能力翻倍 ?</p>\n</section>\n\n</section>','报KET还是PET？开学前这张表帮你5分钟定下来','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYGuP7dgxiL8vp_GEGvmTADE-oaICVoTI21e9m45gxF8','http://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_jpg/j3HgDTfdlibPicLd5Axd9g4ibsGqGibnzh4EVxrZMFxp23ic1la763iaEXTfabbUVb7P0ofA2rduzt1y8jXBAMFADdb22ERQpv9vJCl0YWdgQ657A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg',1,0,0,'ai_auto','KET PET 备考攻略 级别选择','报KET还是PET？5分钟定下来✅','报KET还是PET？5分钟定下来✅\n\n每年开学都有家长问我这个问题，整理清楚了?\n\n? KET（A2）\n→ 小学5年级~初一\n→ 词汇量600-1200个\n→ 备考3-4个月\n\n? PET（B1）\n→ 初一~初三\n→ 词汇量1500-2500个\n→ 备考4-6个月\n\n❌ 最常踩的坑\n孩子成绩不错就直接报PET\n结果写作不会，一次没过，打击信心\n\n✅ 正确做法\n先做一套真题，70%以上再报\nPET写作单独测一次，能写80词再说\n\n评论区告诉我孩子年级+词汇量，帮你判断?\n\n#KET备考 #PET备考 #剑桥英语 #初中英语 #英语备考 #英语学习',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 09:42:03','2026-03-07 10:42:21',1,NULL),(16,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpcA1EI16zPHIxsnJx0PkSkBcYisP1j1b7yaUCwaccPso','Day 1 | 开学打卡：把这5个中式英语换掉，口语立刻地道','Cathy','开学第一周，先把最常用的5个「中式英语」换掉。 每天5分钟，30天后你会发现口语和写作都顺了不少。   今日5组替换          1            I very like English &nbsp;→&nbsp; I rea','<section style=\"font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\'PingFang SC\',\'Microsoft YaHei\',sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:16px;line-height:1.9\">\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px\">\n开学第一周，先把最常用的5个「中式英语」换掉。<br>\n每天5分钟，30天后你会发现口语和写作都顺了不少。\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;padding:2px 0 2px 12px;margin:0 0 18px;line-height:1.4\">今日5组替换</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 14px\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;align-items:flex-start\">\n    <span style=\"min-width:26px;height:26px;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">1</span>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#dc2626;text-decoration:line-through\">I very like English</span> &nbsp;→&nbsp; <strong style=\"color:#16a34a\">I really enjoy English</strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b\">very + 动词 是典型中式思维，enjoy 比 like 更自然</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;align-items:flex-start\">\n    <span style=\"min-width:26px;height:26px;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">2</span>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#dc2626;text-decoration:line-through\">Add oil!</span> &nbsp;→&nbsp; <strong style=\"color:#16a34a\">Come on! / You\'ve got this!</strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b\">「加油」是中文概念，外教听不懂 Add oil</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;align-items:flex-start\">\n    <span style=\"min-width:26px;height:26px;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">3</span>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#dc2626;text-decoration:line-through\">Open the light</span> &nbsp;→&nbsp; <strong style=\"color:#16a34a\">Turn on the light</strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b\">开/关灯永远用 turn on / turn off</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;align-items:flex-start\">\n    <span style=\"min-width:26px;height:26px;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">4</span>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#dc2626;text-decoration:line-through\">Yesterday I went to shopping</span> &nbsp;→&nbsp; <strong style=\"color:#16a34a\">I went shopping yesterday</strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b\">go shopping 不加 to，时间状语放句末更自然</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start\">\n    <span style=\"min-width:26px;height:26px;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">5</span>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#dc2626;text-decoration:line-through\">How are you? Fine, thank you</span> &nbsp;→&nbsp; <strong style=\"color:#16a34a\">Hey, how\'s it going? / Not bad, you?</strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b\">课本式回答早被淘汰了，日常对话更随意</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#f0fdf4;border-left:4px solid #22c55e;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 28px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#15803d\">? 今日打卡任务</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#14532d;line-height:1.8\">用今天学的5个表达各造一个句子，评论区打卡，我来批改 ✏️</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"padding:20px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#7c3aed);border-radius:14px;text-align:center\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:15px;color:#fff;font-weight:600\">? 今日练习已同步到小程序</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);line-height:1.75\">微信搜索【英语陪跑Go】→ 进入打卡 → 完成今日任务<br>坚持21天，备考能力翻倍 ?</p>\n</section>\n\n</section>','Day 1 | 开学打卡：把这5个中式英语换掉，口语立刻地道','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSR5a07xMO7c2WcmestUkK9B-DVcCHIEMCdnF4QisxtA','http://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/j3HgDTfdlibOsicN3tD5UNqsnmVsAISVuwxyA8WNVM8Gbw9LbZvzxPCrWVkPK02ZWzRYCVribpFiaX1cnEmVv8UfvDr6zG8bKHg8VRUSH721SVE/0?wx_fmt=jpeg',1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语打卡 中式英语 口语','','',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 09:42:07','2026-03-07 10:42:21',1,NULL),(17,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpXn84z2B25ghgeECDofxZ68u2Z4YFUHUHd83UXLXEP74','孩子说了这5句英语，外教当场愣住了——你家也有吗？','Cathy','上周有个家长在后台跟我说： 「孩子英语成绩挺好的，但外教课上说了句『I am very 兴奋』，外教愣了5秒……」    哈哈，这种场面太熟悉了。今天整理了5个「外教现场蒙圈」的中式英语，看看你家孩子有几个？   5个让外教沉默的表达','<section style=\"font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\'PingFang SC\',\'Microsoft YaHei\',sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:16px;line-height:1.9\">\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px\">\n上周有个家长在后台跟我说：<br>\n「孩子英语成绩挺好的，但外教课上说了句『I am very 兴奋』，外教愣了5秒……」\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;color:#475569\">\n哈哈，这种场面太熟悉了。今天整理了5个「外教现场蒙圈」的中式英语，看看你家孩子有几个？\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;border-left:4px solid #dc2626;padding:2px 0 2px 12px;margin:0 0 18px;line-height:1.4\">5个让外教沉默的表达</h2>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套备考资料包！</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section style=\"background:#fef2f2;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 14px;border:1px solid #fecaca\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626\">❌ 「I am very 兴奋」</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d\">为什么蒙圈：中英混搭，外教以为你在学说中文</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#15803d\">✅ 地道说法：<strong>I\'m so excited!</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fef2f2;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 14px;border:1px solid #fecaca\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626\">❌ 「My mother got the flu. She is so pain.」</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d\">为什么蒙圈：pain 是名词，不能直接做表语</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#15803d\">✅ 地道说法：<strong>She\'s in a lot of pain. / She\'s feeling unwell.</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fef2f2;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 14px;border:1px solid #fecaca\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626\">❌ 「I want to drink water.」（课堂上大声说）</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d\">为什么蒙圈：直白到像命令，正常该说 May I / Could I</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#15803d\">✅ 地道说法：<strong>May I get some water, please?</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fef2f2;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 14px;border:1px solid #fecaca\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626\">❌ 「The weather is very nice today, right?」（每次开口必说）</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d\">为什么蒙圈：完全课本腔，真实对话很少这样说</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#15803d\">✅ 地道说法：<strong>Great weather, isn\'t it? / Loving this sunshine!</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fef2f2;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 24px;border:1px solid #fecaca\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626\">❌ 「Long time no see!」</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#7f1d1d\">为什么蒙圈：这个其实是从中文直译来的……但现在反而约定俗成了</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#15803d\">✅ 其实：外教<strong>能听懂</strong>，算中式英语里少见的\"合法出圈\"案例 ?</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;color:#475569;font-size:15px\">\n你家孩子说过哪几个？评论区来一起晒晒，说不定我下期专门出一篇「家长群中式英语大赏」?\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"padding:20px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#7c3aed);border-radius:14px;text-align:center\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:15px;color:#fff;font-weight:600\">? 今日练习已同步到小程序</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);line-height:1.75\">微信搜索【英语陪跑Go】→ 进入打卡 → 完成今日任务<br>坚持21天，备考能力翻倍 ?</p>\n</section>\n\n</section>','孩子说了这5句英语，外教当场愣住了——你家也有吗？','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpakvOz-vDE8IhKBoKGBI5grTgxa3xbHkE4t3kuNCJkZI','http://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/j3HgDTfdlibNytUygdUqqt4fnmO9NOeWiaEicRJClfMoSZclY3Piak3TnkM6epz7wbfeCc5LXKZAaYJiacsenCUm6xKtw2qbDdqsEdmquSmRgOTQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg',1,0,0,'ai_auto','中式英语 外教 趣味','','',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 09:42:10','2026-03-07 10:42:21',1,NULL),(18,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSuilkWVhYOUWpkR4XlQsMBitlPnDOFX2CF88sr5wDih','PET 高频短语 11-20 | 阅读写作提分必备','Cathy','✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载  ? 粉丝福利关注公众号，回复「PET短语」，获取完整100个PET高频短语合集 PDF（含例句+真题出处）！? 进度：20/100（已完成 20%）  11–20 短语逐个拆解  11. take part i','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「PET短语」</strong>，获取完整100个PET高频短语合集 PDF（含例句+真题出处）！</p><p style=\"text-align:center;font-size:13px;opacity:0.88;margin:8px 0 0\">? 进度：20/100（已完成 20%）</p></section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">11–20 短语逐个拆解</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">11. take part in</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>参加，参与</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She took part in the school speech contest and won second place.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她参加了学校演讲比赛，获得第二名。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">12. look forward to</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>期待（to+doing）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I\'m looking forward to hearing from you soon.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 期待尽快收到你的回复。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">13. make sure</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>确保，确认</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Make sure you arrive at the exam centre at least 15 minutes early.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 确保至少提前15分钟到达考场。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">14. be responsible for</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>对……负责</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Each student is responsible for keeping their study area clean.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 每个学生负责保持自己学习区域整洁。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">15. in order to</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>为了（目的状语）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? In order to improve her writing, she read one English article daily.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 为了提升写作，她每天读一篇英文文章。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">16. get used to</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>习惯于（过程）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? After a month abroad, she got used to speaking English every day.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 出国一个月后，她习惯了每天说英语。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">17. pay attention to</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>注意，关注</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Please pay attention to the instructions before you start.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 开始前请仔细阅读说明。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">18. as well as</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>以及，还有（更正式）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The course covers reading as well as writing and speaking skills.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 课程涵盖阅读以及写作和口语技能。</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">19. deal with</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>处理，应对</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? How do you deal with stress before an important exam?</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你如何应对重要考试前的压力？</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">20. be willing to</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>愿意做某事</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? A good team member should be willing to help others when needed.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 好的团队成员应该愿意在需要时帮助他人。</p></section>\n\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">任选3个短语各造一个句子，评论区打卡，我来批改 ✏️<br>坚持21天打卡，送完整100短语 PDF（回复「PET短语」也可直接领取）</p></section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几个短语？</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：PET 高频短语 21-30 | 阅读写作提分必备</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','PET高频短语11-20','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpY2copBwW_ZlCibVSSuUEsHBAYCie78LvPpzyrHJEf9H','http://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_jpg/j3HgDTfdlibPVpBsiaY8UbOJsGXniacXkqyQAS97lrn2g80YNEx3n01g5VI7l4E7XwPFcA6By0aBU4S6NxGBjGJTHhm7IXyKlVKA8s5Bic2iaE1g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg',1,0,0,'ai_auto','PET 高频短语 备考','PET高频短语11-20 | 每天5分钟，阅读写作都提分✅','PET高频短语第二组！\n\n11. take part in（参与）\n12. look forward to（期待）\n13. make sure（确保）\n14. be responsible for（负责）\n15. in order to（为了）\n16. get used to（习惯）\n17. pay attention to（注意）\n18. as well as（以及）\n19. deal with（处理）\n20. be willing to（愿意）\n\n关注公众号【英语陪跑Go】回复「PET短语」领100短语PDF\n\n#PET备考 #剑桥英语 #英语短语 #初中英语',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 09:57:54','2026-03-07 10:36:44',1,NULL),(19,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpXn84z2B25ghgeECDofxZ68u2Z4YFUHUHd83UXLXEP74','PET写作必备 | 邮件万能模板+真题示范，4月考试直接用','Cathy','PET写作邮件万能模板','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n4月25日PET考试，报名刚截止——现在开始备考还来得及。<br>\n写作Part 2是很多同学丢分最多的一项，今天把<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">邮件写作万能模板</strong>全部整理出来，照着练，直接用。\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">PET写作 Part 2 是什么？</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n考试要求写一封<strong>约100词的邮件/便条</strong>，给出3个要点，全部必须覆盖。<br>\n评分标准：<strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">内容覆盖 + 语言准确 + 表达得体</strong>，三者缺一。\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「PET写作」</strong>，获取完整PET写作模板+高分句型资料！</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">万能框架：5段式结构</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">① 称呼行</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>写信人和收件人关系决定称呼</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Dear Tom, &nbsp;/&nbsp; Dear Ms. Green, &nbsp;/&nbsp; Hi Sarah,</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 认识的人用名字，不认识的用 Dear Sir/Madam</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">② 开头：说明写信目的</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>万能句型（3选1）：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? I am writing to tell you about ...</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? I am writing to invite you to ...</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I am writing because I need your help with ...</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">③ 主体：覆盖3个要点</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>高分连接词：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? First of all, ... &nbsp;/&nbsp; Also, ... &nbsp;/&nbsp; In addition, ...</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I think ... because ... &nbsp;/&nbsp; I suggest that ...</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 3个要点各写1-2句，不要遗漏任何一个</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">④ 结尾：礼貌收束</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>万能结尾句（必背）：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? I look forward to hearing from you.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? Please let me know if you have any questions.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I hope you can come / I hope this helps.</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">⑤ 落款</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? Best wishes, [你的名字]</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Yours, [你的名字] &nbsp;/&nbsp; See you soon, [名字]</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">真题示范（直接套用）</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:15px;color:#555;margin:15px 0\">\n<strong>题目要点：</strong>邀请朋友来你家参加派对 / 告诉他时间地点 / 说明需要带什么\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:14px 16px;margin:18px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2c3e50;margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:bold\">示范答案（约100词）：</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#444;line-height:1.9;margin:0\">\n  Dear Lisa,<br><br>\n  I am writing to invite you to my birthday party. It will be on Saturday 15th March at 6 pm at my house — 25 Park Road.<br><br>\n  We are going to have dinner together and then play some games. I think it will be really fun!<br><br>\n  Could you bring some snacks if possible? Something sweet would be great.<br><br>\n  I look forward to seeing you there. Please let me know if you can come.<br><br>\n  Best wishes,<br>\n  Tom\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  用上面的框架写一封邮件，主题自选（邀请朋友/推荐一本书/感谢某人），约80-100词。<br>评论区打卡，我来批改 ✏️\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：写完的同学在这里晒出来</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：PET口语 Part3 万能扩展法</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','PET写作邮件万能模板','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpbINbtibSqnep_k0f4kyDJuqrbxnuL_4MnBmH1oxmBTX','http://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/j3HgDTfdlibNfW62eFnYDsULVFVbmc0XgB7vjicjfMuPsF0r42PwwicLKlDYwpLfeq2Pac8Ro12UrYoKFH4PWxPtHf3nIlonYe3jia52UwntvCs/0?wx_fmt=jpeg',1,0,0,'ai_auto','PET 写作 邮件 备考','PET写作邮件模板 | 5段式框架+真题示范✅','PET写作Part 2 邮件题，很多同学在这里丢分！\n\n整理了万能5段式框架?\n\n① 称呼行：Dear Tom / Hi Sarah\n② 开头：I am writing to tell you about...\n③ 主体：3个要点都要覆盖！\n   First of all... / Also... / In addition...\n④ 结尾：I look forward to hearing from you.\n⑤ 落款：Best wishes, [名字]\n\n记住：3个要点一个不能漏\n字数控制在100词左右\n\n关注公众号【英语陪跑Go】回复「PET写作」领完整模板资料\n\n#PET备考 #剑桥英语 #英语写作 #初中英语 #PET写作',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:26:55','2026-03-07 10:42:21',1,NULL),(20,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpXGqNgcMSN2Qs1Or_OVJC27rVHZz9hPDIJo7COK9fdzH','AI帮孩子学英语？这3个用法是真有效，家长别走弯路','Cathy','AI帮孩子学英语三个有效用法','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n最近后台有很多家长问：「孩子用AI学英语，真的有用吗？」<br>\n答案是：<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">有用，但要用对地方。</strong><br>\n用错了，只是让孩子多了个玩具；用对了，效率能翻倍。\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">① 口语对话练习——最该用的场景</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套学习资料包！</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n大多数孩子最缺的不是单词，而是<strong>开口说</strong>的机会。<br>\nAI可以随时陪练，不会嘲笑发音，不会不耐烦。\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">✅ 正确用法：给AI一个角色</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">跟AI说：<em style=\"color:#555\">「You are a barista. I want to order coffee. Let\'s practice.」</em></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">AI会扮演咖啡师，孩子练习真实场景对话，比背单词有用10倍。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#fdf2f2;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 8px\">❌ 错误用法：直接问答案</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">让AI直接翻译/写作业，孩子自己啥也没练到。</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">② 写作批改——节省家长时间</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n孩子写完一篇英语作文，拿去给AI批改，要求它：\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>给AI的指令模板：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? \"Please correct my English essay. Point out grammar errors and suggest better expressions. Don\'t rewrite it for me, just give hints.\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:6px 0 0\">— 关键：让AI给提示，不让它直接重写，孩子要自己修改</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">③ 单词记忆——让AI出题</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n背单词最怕：背了就忘，忘了再背。<br>\n让AI用单词<strong>造句、出填空题、编小故事</strong>，比死记强得多。\n</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>示例指令：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? \"Make a short story using these 5 words: exhausted, eventually, suggest, habit, benefit.\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:6px 0 0\">— 孩子读完故事，单词在语境里就记住了</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 家长记住这个原则</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  AI是<strong>练习的对象</strong>，不是<strong>完成作业的工具</strong>。<br>\n  让孩子主动跟AI说英语，而不是让AI帮孩子说英语。\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区：你家孩子现在用AI学英语了吗？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','AI帮孩子学英语三个有效用法','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSmYwVgGSFSHuN76e1Fm5Ug9wkv-mfTqnHHqu9TJTAm8',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','AI英语学习热点','AI学英语？这3个用法真有效✅ 别再让孩子用错了','最近好多家长问我，孩子用AI学英语有没有用\n\n答案是：有用，但要用对地方！\n\n✅ 正确用法1：口语对话练习\n给AI一个角色让孩子跟它说英语\n比如：You are a barista, let\'s practice ordering coffee\n\n✅ 正确用法2：写作批改\n让AI找错误给提示，孩子自己改\n不要让AI直接帮写！\n\n✅ 正确用法3：单词造句记忆\n让AI用5个单词编故事\n在语境里记单词效率翻倍\n\n❌ 错误用法：让AI帮孩子完成作业\n那是在帮倒忙\n\nAI是练习的对象，不是完成作业的工具\n\n关注公众号【英语陪跑Go】获取更多实用方法\n\n#英语学习 #AI学习 #英语教育 #亲子英语 #英语启蒙',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:42:21','2026-03-07 10:54:59',1,NULL),(21,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpXGqNgcMSN2Qs1Or_OVJC27rVHZz9hPDIJo7COK9fdzH','孩子说英语总被外教皱眉？这5个中式英语，改掉一个提升一档','Cathy','✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载    中式英语不是语法错，而是「听起来不像英语母语」的那种微妙感。 外教不会当场纠正，但会在心里默默打分。今天来看5个最高频的。   5个让外教微微皱眉的表达     ? 粉丝福利   关注公众号，回复「口语」，','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n中式英语不是语法错，而是<strong>「听起来不像英语母语」</strong>的那种微妙感。<br>\n外教不会当场纠正，但会在心里默默打分。今天来看5个最高频的。\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个让外教微微皱眉的表达</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取PET 口语备考资料+地道表达手册！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">1. very + 情绪词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ I am very excited. / I am very happy.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ I\'m thrilled! / I\'m overjoyed! / I\'m delighted!</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:0\">— 情绪词本身就是\"极度\"的，再加very反而显得小学级别</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">2. study hard</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ I need to study hard.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ I need to work hard on my studies. / I need to put in more effort.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:0\">— \"study hard\"本身没错，但母语者更自然的说法是这两种</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">3. open the light</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ Can you open the light?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ Can you turn on the light? / Switch on the light?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:0\">— 灯/电视/空调/水 全部用 turn on / turn off，不是 open/close</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">4. do sports</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ I like to do sports every day.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ I like playing sports. / I exercise every day.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:0\">— \"do sports\"是中式直译，母语者说 play sports 或 exercise</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">5. body not comfortable</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ My body is not comfortable today.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ I\'m not feeling well. / I feel a bit under the weather.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:0\">— 身体不舒服直接说 not feeling well，body uncomfortable 听起来像\"椅子坐着不舒服\"</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 改掉的关键</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  不是记单词，而是记<strong>搭配</strong>。<br>\n  每天改一个，一周后说话的感觉就不一样了。\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天你改掉了哪一个？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','5个最常见中式英语纠错','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYWDz8dpR09Wj6ijm7yYJ_ru_bwYdyyUAFq7TEB6uhWt',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语口语知识','外教皱眉？这5个中式英语改掉，马上地道✨','孩子英语说不地道，不一定是单词少\n\n很可能是这5个中式英语在拉分?\n\n❌ very excited → ✅ thrilled\n❌ study hard → ✅ put in more effort\n❌ open the light → ✅ turn on the light\n❌ do sports → ✅ play sports\n❌ body not comfortable → ✅ not feeling well\n\n改掉一个，说话的感觉就不一样了\n\n记住：不是背单词，是记搭配\n每天改一个，一周后明显不同\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】，每天一个地道表达\n\n#英语口语 #中式英语 #英语纠错 #英语学习 #亲子英语',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:42:21','2026-03-07 10:54:59',1,NULL),(22,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpXGqNgcMSN2Qs1Or_OVJC27rVHZz9hPDIJo7COK9fdzH','英语写作总是\"and and and\"？5类连接词用起来，文章立刻有层次','Cathy','✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载    判断一篇英语作文好不好，看什么？ 老师看的第一件事就是：连接词用对了没有。 全文只有 and / but / so 三个字，再好的内容也显得单薄。   5类连接词，每类背2个就够用     ? 粉丝福利','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n判断一篇英语作文好不好，看什么？<br>\n老师看的第一件事就是：<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">连接词用对了没有。</strong><br>\n全文只有 and / but / so 三个字，再好的内容也显得单薄。\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5类连接词，每类背2个就够用</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取PET 写作备考资料+万能模板！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">① 递进（不止一个理由）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ It is good and it is cheap.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ Not only is it good, but it is also affordable.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? Furthermore, the price is reasonable.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 用：furthermore / in addition / not only...but also / moreover</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">② 转折（但是、然而）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ It is useful but expensive.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ It is useful. However, it comes at a high cost.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? On the other hand, some people disagree.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 用：however / on the other hand / nevertheless / despite this</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">③ 因果（所以、因为）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ I was tired so I slept early.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ As a result, I went to bed earlier than usual.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? Due to the heavy rain, the match was cancelled.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 用：as a result / therefore / due to / consequently</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">④ 举例（比如、例如）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ I like many sports, like swimming.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ I enjoy various sports, such as swimming and cycling.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? For instance, many students find reading helpful.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 用：for example / for instance / such as / to illustrate</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 8px\">⑤ 总结（最后、总之）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;margin:0 0 4px\">❌ So, I think this is good.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ In conclusion, I strongly believe that...</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 4px\">? To sum up, the benefits far outweigh the drawbacks.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 用：in conclusion / to sum up / overall / in summary</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  用这5类连接词各造一句，评论区晒出来，我来批改 ✏️<br>\n  坚持一周，写作文时连接词自然就用出来了。\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：5个连接词各造一句</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语写作开头结尾万能句</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','写作5类连接词：递进转折因果举例总结','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpQvs3NzkhItBu73Dwi-S7r_XPfYWAKVY_x7U2PW_pv1y',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语写作知识','写作只会and/but/so？5类连接词用起来?','判断英语作文好不好\n老师第一眼看的就是：连接词！\n\n5类连接词，每类背2个就够用?\n\n① 递进：furthermore / in addition\n② 转折：however / on the other hand\n③ 因果：as a result / therefore\n④ 举例：for example / such as\n⑤ 总结：in conclusion / to sum up\n\n用了这些词，文章立刻有层次感\n\n今日打卡：5类各造一句，评论区晒出来\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】，每天英语干货不停\n\n#英语写作 #连接词 #英语学习 #写作技巧 #英语干货',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:42:21','2026-03-07 10:54:59',1,NULL),(23,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYaBBHMhNUULlOx1VyrsLjVvplTO1YxCp2tpe0X_eGeR','2026年最火的5个科技英语词，懂了这些你就不OUT了','Cathy','2026科技热词英语：具身智能vibe coding智能体数字孪生AI幻觉','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最近「具身智能」「RLHF」「vibe coding」这些词刷屏了——这些概念，英语里怎么说？</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天整理了2026年最流行的5个科技英语词，懂了这些，和外国人聊天不再一脸茫然。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个2026年高频科技英语词</h2>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套学习资料！</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. Embodied AI（具身智能）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>能感知和操控物理世界的AI</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Embodied AI robots can now fold laundry and navigate homes.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 具身AI机器人现在能叠衣服、在家里自己走动了</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 不是AI本身，而是\'有身体的AI\'</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. Vibe coding（氛围编程）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>靠描述感觉让AI写代码，而不是自己写</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He built the whole app with vibe coding — just describing what he wanted.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他全程用氛围编程做的这个App，只是描述了自己想要什么</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 2025年底流行起来，用于描述AI辅助编程方式</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. Agentic AI（智能体AI）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>能自己制定计划、执行多步任务的AI</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Agentic AI can book flights, write emails, and summarize reports — all by itself.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 智能体AI能自己订机票、写邮件、总结报告</p>\n  \n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Digital twin（数字孪生）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>现实世界物体或系统的虚拟镜像</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The factory uses a digital twin to test changes before applying them in real life.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 工厂用数字孪生在现实操作前先模拟测试</p>\n  \n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. Hallucination（AI幻觉）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>AI自信地给出错误信息</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The chatbot gave wrong directions — a typical AI hallucination.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这个聊天机器人给了错误的指路——典型的AI幻觉</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 面试/考试聊到AI时，这个词用出来加分</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选其中一个词，用英语造一个句子，评论区见！<br>明天还有5个热词，记得关注。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语里最容易说错的5个动词搭配</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','2026科技热词英语：具身智能vibe coding智能体数字孪生AI幻觉','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpfRj4seafI0CAChgkJzXxARcvT-VIViVdaaYg9mergNm',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','热点英语科技词汇','2026最火科技英语词汇✨ 「具身智能」「vibe coding」怎么说','最近这些词刷屏了，英语怎么说？\n\n? Embodied AI = 具身智能\n? Vibe coding = 氛围编程（靠描述感觉让AI写代码）\n? Agentic AI = 智能体AI\n? Digital twin = 数字孪生\n? Hallucination = AI幻觉（AI自信地给出错误信息）\n\n下次跟外国人聊AI，这5个词直接用！\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】，每天一个热点英语\n\n#英语学习 #科技英语 #英语词汇 #AI英语 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:54:59','2026-03-07 11:07:11',1,NULL),(24,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYaBBHMhNUULlOx1VyrsLjVvplTO1YxCp2tpe0X_eGeR','这5个动词搭配，中国人99%说错过——改掉立刻地道','Cathy','动词搭配：make do区别 take a photo catch a cold play a role','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">学英语最难的不是单词，是<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">搭配</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">同样一件事，中国人说出来外国人听不懂，不是因为词不对，是因为动词搭配错了。<br>今天5个最常见的动词搭配错误，改掉一个提升一档。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个动词搭配，中国人99%说错</h2>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取英语口语备考资料+地道表达手册！</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. make / do 的区别</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>make=创造出新东西；do=执行一件事</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I need to make a decision. / I need to do my homework.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我需要做决定。/ 我需要做作业。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ do a decision / make homework 都是错的</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. take a photo（拍照）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 shoot a photo，不是 do a photo</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can you take a photo of me in front of the tower?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你能在塔前帮我拍张照吗？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ take = 拿走，拍照就是\'拿走\'光线</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. have a look（看一眼）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 take a look at...，两种都对，但搭配不同</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can I have a look at your notes?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我能看一下你的笔记吗？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ have a look at = take a look at，但不能说 do a look</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. catch a cold（感冒）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 get cold，不是 have a cold weather</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I caught a cold last week and stayed home.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我上周感冒了，待在家里。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ get a cold 也对；cold weather是冷天气，完全不同</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. play a role（扮演角色/起作用）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 do a role，不是 act a role</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Technology plays a huge role in modern education.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 科技在现代教育中起到了巨大作用。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ play = 演奏/玩耍/扮演，全都用play</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 改掉的方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">不用死记，每次说英语时注意动词是哪个。<br>犯错了没关系，发现了就改，多说几次自然就对了。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语写作5类连接词速查表</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','动词搭配：make do区别 take a photo catch a cold play a role','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUMNjgKRijuP15fgoPv9AZv8i_4zURAHE8_TG0row8cZ',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语口语动词搭配','动词搭配错了不自知？这5个99%中国人说错过❌','学英语最难的是动词搭配！\n\n❌ do a decision → ✅ make a decision\n❌ shoot a photo → ✅ take a photo\n❌ do a look → ✅ have a look\n❌ get cold → ✅ catch a cold\n❌ do a role → ✅ play a role\n\n记口诀：\nmake=创造 / do=执行 / take=拿走 / catch=抓住 / play=扮演\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天英语干货不停\n\n#英语口语 #动词搭配 #英语错误 #英语学习 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:54:59','2026-03-07 11:07:11',1,NULL),(25,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYaBBHMhNUULlOx1VyrsLjVvplTO1YxCp2tpe0X_eGeR','英语写作连接词速查表｜5类20个，收藏这一篇就够了','Cathy','英语写作连接词：递进furthermore 转折however 因果therefore 举例forexample 总结inconclusion','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语作文里，连接词用得好不好，老师一眼就能看出来。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">不是说要用多难的词——而是要用<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">对的词</strong>。<br>今天整理了一份连接词速查表，收藏备用。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">连接词速查表：5类20个</h2>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作备考资料+连接词完整版PDF！</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">①. 递进（表示更进一步）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>not only...but also / furthermore / in addition / moreover / besides</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Furthermore, this approach saves both time and money.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 此外，这个方法既省时又省钱。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ 不要总用 and，and太平淡</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">②. 转折（表示但是）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>however / nevertheless / on the other hand / despite / although</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? However, not everyone agrees with this idea.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 然而，不是每个人都同意这个看法。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ 不要只用 but，but显得很口语</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">③. 因果（表示所以/因为）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>therefore / as a result / consequently / due to / because of</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? As a result, many students improved their scores significantly.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 结果，很多学生的成绩明显提高了。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ so 太口语，正式写作少用</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">④. 举例（表示比如）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>for example / for instance / such as / to illustrate / namely</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? For instance, many countries have adopted this policy.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 例如，许多国家已经采纳了这项政策。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ for example 和 for instance 可以互换</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">⑤. 总结（表示最后/总之）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>in conclusion / to sum up / overall / in summary / to conclude</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? In conclusion, I believe technology brings more benefits than drawbacks.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 总之，我认为科技带来的好处多于坏处。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ 结尾段必用，显得有逻辑</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选5类各一个连接词，每类写一句话，评论区打卡！<br>我来批改，免费 ✏️</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语口语最常用的10个反问句</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','英语写作连接词：递进furthermore 转折however 因果therefore 举例forexample 总结inconclusion','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpRVP-2P_2EAPYS2ouFBXTNZzfRVQGO1tRq4UIBCiX0M8',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语写作连接词','英语写作连接词速查表? 5类20个全在这里','写作连接词一直搞混？\n\n收藏这张速查表?\n\n① 递进：furthermore / in addition / moreover\n② 转折：however / nevertheless / despite\n③ 因果：therefore / as a result / due to\n④ 举例：for example / for instance / such as\n⑤ 总结：in conclusion / to sum up / overall\n\n每类记2个就够用！\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天写作干货\n\n#英语写作 #连接词 #英语学习 #写作技巧 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 10:54:59','2026-03-07 11:07:11',1,NULL),(26,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUlAhGEFXthW7RHWNehENnTlbS2aQNJI62OL2p8do6Qr','2026年最火的5个科技英语词，懂了这些你就不OUT了','Cathy','2026科技热词英语：具身智能vibe coding智能体数字孪生AI幻觉','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最近「具身智能」「RLHF」「vibe coding」这些词刷屏了——这些概念，英语里怎么说？</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天整理了2026年最流行的5个科技英语词，懂了这些，和外国人聊天不再一脸茫然。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个2026年高频科技英语词</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套学习资料！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. Embodied AI（具身智能）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>能感知和操控物理世界的AI</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Embodied AI robots can now fold laundry and navigate homes.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 具身AI机器人现在能叠衣服、在家里自己走动了</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 不是AI本身，而是\'有身体的AI\'</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. Vibe coding（氛围编程）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>靠描述感觉让AI写代码，而不是自己写</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He built the whole app with vibe coding — just describing what he wanted.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他全程用氛围编程做的这个App，只是描述了自己想要什么</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 2025年底流行起来，用于描述AI辅助编程方式</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. Agentic AI（智能体AI）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>能自己制定计划、执行多步任务的AI</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Agentic AI can book flights, write emails, and summarize reports — all by itself.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 智能体AI能自己订机票、写邮件、总结报告</p>  </section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Digital twin（数字孪生）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>现实世界物体或系统的虚拟镜像</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The factory uses a digital twin to test changes before applying them in real life.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 工厂用数字孪生在现实操作前先模拟测试</p>  </section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. Hallucination（AI幻觉）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>AI自信地给出错误信息</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The chatbot gave wrong directions — a typical AI hallucination.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这个聊天机器人给了错误的指路——典型的AI幻觉</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 面试/考试聊到AI时，这个词用出来加分</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选其中一个词，用英语造一个句子，评论区见！<br>明天还有5个热词，记得关注。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语里最容易说错的5个动词搭配</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','2026科技热词英语：具身智能vibe coding智能体数字孪生AI幻觉','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpTqhaSMc3upRi91gavRa_FSoD80fzzfG-c8e-x23ystk',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','热点英语科技词汇','2026最火科技英语词汇✨ 「具身智能」「vibe coding」怎么说','最近这些词刷屏了，英语怎么说？\\n\\n? Embodied AI = 具身智能\\n? Vibe coding = 氛围编程（靠描述感觉让AI写代码）\\n? Agentic AI = 智能体AI\\n? Digital twin = 数字孪生\\n? Hallucination = AI幻觉（AI自信地给出错误信息）\\n\\n下次跟外国人聊AI，这5个词直接用！\\n\\n关注【英语陪跑Go】，每天一个热点英语\\n\\n#英语学习 #科技英语 #英语词汇 #AI英语 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:07:11','2026-03-07 11:28:12',1,NULL),(27,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUlAhGEFXthW7RHWNehENnTlbS2aQNJI62OL2p8do6Qr','这5个动词搭配，中国人99%说错过——改掉立刻地道','Cathy','动词搭配：make do区别 take a photo catch a cold play a role','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">学英语最难的不是单词，是<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">搭配</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">同样一件事，中国人说出来外国人听不懂，不是因为词不对，是因为动词搭配错了。<br>今天5个最常见的动词搭配错误，改掉一个提升一档。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个动词搭配，中国人99%说错</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取英语口语备考资料+地道表达手册！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. make / do 的区别</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>make=创造出新东西；do=执行一件事</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I need to make a decision. / I need to do my homework.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我需要做决定。/ 我需要做作业。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ do a decision / make homework 都是错的</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. take a photo（拍照）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 shoot a photo，不是 do a photo</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can you take a photo of me in front of the tower?</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你能在塔前帮我拍张照吗？</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ take = 拿走，拍照就是\'拿走\'光线</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. have a look（看一眼）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 take a look at...，两种都对，但搭配不同</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can I have a look at your notes?</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我能看一下你的笔记吗？</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ have a look at = take a look at，但不能说 do a look</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. catch a cold（感冒）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 get cold，不是 have a cold weather</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I caught a cold last week and stayed home.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我上周感冒了，待在家里。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ get a cold 也对；cold weather是冷天气，完全不同</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. play a role（扮演角色/起作用）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>不是 do a role，不是 act a role</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Technology plays a huge role in modern education.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 科技在现代教育中起到了巨大作用。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ play = 演奏/玩耍/扮演，全都用play</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 改掉的方法</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">不用死记，每次说英语时注意动词是哪个。<br>犯错了没关系，发现了就改，多说几次自然就对了。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语写作5类连接词速查表</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','动词搭配：make do区别 take a photo catch a cold play a role','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpdAwHWMN4jAKj7LsMGW9V5kIq4wZmmLv9OPIl0MrXf6A',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语口语动词搭配','动词搭配错了不自知？这5个99%中国人说错过❌','学英语最难的是动词搭配！\\n\\n❌ do a decision → ✅ make a decision\\n❌ shoot a photo → ✅ take a photo\\n❌ do a look → ✅ have a look\\n❌ get cold → ✅ catch a cold\\n❌ do a role → ✅ play a role\\n\\n记口诀：\\nmake=创造 / do=执行 / take=拿走 / catch=抓住 / play=扮演\\n\\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天英语干货不停\\n\\n#英语口语 #动词搭配 #英语错误 #英语学习 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:07:11','2026-03-07 11:28:12',1,NULL),(28,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUlAhGEFXthW7RHWNehENnTlbS2aQNJI62OL2p8do6Qr','英语写作连接词速查表｜5类20个，收藏这一篇就够了','Cathy','英语写作连接词：递进furthermore 转折however 因果therefore','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语作文里，连接词用得好不好，老师一眼就能看出来。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">不是说要用多难的词——而是要用<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">对的词</strong>。<br>今天整理了一份连接词速查表，收藏备用。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">连接词速查表：5类20个</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作备考资料+连接词完整版PDF！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">①. 递进（表示更进一步）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>not only...but also / furthermore / in addition / moreover / besides</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Furthermore, this approach saves both time and money.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 此外，这个方法既省时又省钱。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ 不要总用 and，and太平淡</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">②. 转折（表示但是）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>however / nevertheless / on the other hand / despite / although</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? However, not everyone agrees with this idea.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 然而，不是每个人都同意这个看法。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ 不要只用 but，but显得很口语</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">③. 因果（表示所以/因为）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>therefore / as a result / consequently / due to / because of</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? As a result, many students improved their scores significantly.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 结果，很多学生的成绩明显提高了。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ so 太口语，正式写作少用</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">④. 举例（表示比如）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>for example / for instance / such as / to illustrate / namely</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? For instance, many countries have adopted this policy.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 例如，许多国家已经采纳了这项政策。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ for example 和 for instance 可以互换</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">⑤. 总结（表示最后/总之）</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>in conclusion / to sum up / overall / in summary / to conclude</p>  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? In conclusion, I believe technology brings more benefits than drawbacks.</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 总之，我认为科技带来的好处多于坏处。</p>  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ✅ 结尾段必用，显得有逻辑</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p>  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选5类各一个连接词，每类写一句话，评论区打卡！<br>我来批改，免费 ✏️</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语口语最常用的10个反问句</p>  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','英语写作连接词：递进furthermore 转折however 因果therefore','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpcXDmXz0i1c9MC2eVjNncm0Zqo2xyfQ6HJj-3MwUjT2F',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语写作连接词','英语写作连接词速查表? 5类20个全在这里','写作连接词一直搞混？\\n\\n收藏这张速查表?\\n\\n① 递进：furthermore / in addition / moreover\\n② 转折：however / nevertheless / despite\\n③ 因果：therefore / as a result / due to\\n④ 举例：for example / for instance / such as\\n⑤ 总结：in conclusion / to sum up / overall\\n\\n每类记2个就够用！\\n\\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天写作干货\\n\\n#英语写作 #连接词 #英语学习 #写作技巧 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:07:11','2026-03-07 11:28:12',1,NULL),(30,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpb1yJXLqDN8rdmJQSl0rr53YIHefVZez3kL9exJWSXq6','2026年最火英语口头禅，听懂这5个才算跟上了','Cathy','2026流行英语口头禅：it gives me the ick / no cap / slay / let him cook / understood the assignment','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">每隔一段时间，英语世界都会涌现一批新的口头禅。<br>2026年最流行的这5个，你听过几个？</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天整理出来，不只是知道意思，还要知道怎么用、用在哪。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2026年最火英语口头禅</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套学习资料！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. It gives me the ick</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>让我感到莫名反感/不适</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He chews with his mouth open — it gives me the ick.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他吃东西嘴巴不闭，让我很不舒服。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ick = 恶心感，形容对某人/某事突然失去好感</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. No cap</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>我没在骗你 / 说真的</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? That movie was incredible, no cap.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 那部电影真的太好看了，我没骗你。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ cap = 说谎；no cap = 不吹牛，就是事实</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. Slay</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>太厉害了 / 完全征服</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She walked in and absolutely slayed the presentation.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她走进去，那场演讲直接拿捏了。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 原意=杀死，这里是褒义，表示\'完全做到了\'</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Let him cook</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>让他发挥 / 别打扰他</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Don\'t interrupt — just let him cook.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 别打断，让他发挥就行。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 2024年起流行，来自做饭的隐喻</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. Understood the assignment</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>完全领会了 / 做到位了</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She wore a full Victorian dress to the costume party — understood the assignment.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她穿了完整的维多利亚裙子去主题派对——完全领会精髓。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ assignment = 任务；表示某人把事情做得非常到位</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 用法小提示</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">这5个都是口语/社交媒体用语，正式场合不用。<br>但听懂它们，和外国朋友聊天就不会一脸茫然了。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语里的5个高频误用动词</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','2026流行英语口头禅：it gives me the ick / no cap / slay / let him cook / understood the assignment','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpTEjmIdg0C9V6fNWRwyrloe810imNwCU1TeSF-qU5rGY',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','热点英语口语流行词','2026最火英语口头禅 ? 听懂这5个才算跟上了','你知道这些话是什么意思吗？\n\n「It gives me the ick」→ 让我莫名反感\n「No cap」→ 说真的，没骗你\n「Slay」→ 太厉害了，完全拿捏\n「Let him cook」→ 让他发挥，别打扰\n「Understood the assignment」→ 完全领会了\n\n这5个是2026年英语社交媒体最高频的口头禅\n听懂了，和外国朋友聊天不再一脸茫然～\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天英语干货\n\n#英语口语 #流行英语 #英语学习 #英语干货',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:28:12','2026-03-07 11:43:48',1,NULL),(31,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpb1yJXLqDN8rdmJQSl0rr53YIHefVZez3kL9exJWSXq6','这5个动词，中国人最容易搞混——看完对比例句直接改','Cathy','高频误用动词：borrow/lend区别 tell/say区别 discuss不加about reach不加to rise/raise区别','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语动词用错，往往是因为<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">直接从中文翻译过来</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">下面5个动词是中国人最容易误用的，每个都有对比例句，看完直接改。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个高频误用动词</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取英语口语资料+地道动词搭配手册！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. borrow vs. lend</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>borrow = 我借（向别人借）；lend = 借给（把自己的给别人）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can I borrow your pen? / Can you lend me your pen?</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我能借一下你的笔吗？ / 你能把笔借我吗？</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ Can you borrow me your pen? → 逻辑混乱，这句话不通</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. tell vs. say</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>tell = 告诉某人；say = 说（不一定有对象）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She told me the truth. / She said she was tired.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她告诉了我实情。 / 她说她累了。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ She told that she was tired. → tell 后面必须接人</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. discuss vs. discuss about</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>discuss 本身已含\'关于\'，后面不加 about</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We discussed the plan for an hour.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们讨论了一个小时的计划。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ We discussed about the plan. → about 多余，去掉</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. reach vs. arrive</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>reach 直接加地点；arrive 需要 at/in</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We reached the hotel at 9 pm. / We arrived at the hotel at 9 pm.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们晚上9点到达了酒店。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ We reached to the hotel. → reach 后不加 to</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. rise vs. raise</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>rise = 自己升起（不及物）；raise = 举起/提高（及物，需要宾语）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The sun rises every morning. / Please raise your hand.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 太阳每天升起。 / 请举手。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ Please rise your hand. → raise 才能带宾语</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆方法</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">遇到这5个动词，先问自己：<br>① 动作是自己做还是对别人做？<br>② 后面有没有宾语？<br>想清楚这两点，基本不会再用错。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语写作：让段落更有逻辑的5个句式</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','高频误用动词：borrow/lend区别 tell/say区别 discuss不加about reach不加to rise/raise区别','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpZEPnGMAEfdSmo7XZt0no7J09A1AIOKxFjxuu8wTmMOQ',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语口语动词搭配','这5个英语动词，中国人99%搞混过❌','你有没有说过这些错误？\n\n❌ Can you borrow me your pen?\n✅ Can you lend me your pen?\n\n❌ She told that she was tired.\n✅ She said she was tired.\n\n❌ We discussed about the plan.\n✅ We discussed the plan.\n\n❌ We reached to the hotel.\n✅ We reached the hotel.\n\n❌ Please rise your hand.\n✅ Please raise your hand.\n\n每个都是高频错误，改掉立刻地道！\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天英语干货\n\n#英语口语 #动词搭配 #英语错误 #英语学习',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:28:12','2026-03-07 11:43:48',1,NULL),(32,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpb1yJXLqDN8rdmJQSl0rr53YIHefVZez3kL9exJWSXq6','英语作文段落不够有力？这5个句式套上去，逻辑感立刻来了','Cathy','写作高分句式：It is essential that / Not only but also / While it is true that / This suggests that / In the long run','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语作文分数高不高，很大程度看<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">段落内部的逻辑</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">光有连接词不够，还需要这5个句式来撑起论证。每个都配例句，直接套用。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">让段落更有逻辑的5个句式</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取英语写作资料+高分句式模板！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. It is + adj. + that ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>强调某件事的性质，开门见山</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? It is essential that students develop good study habits early.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 学生尽早养成良好的学习习惯至关重要。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 比直接说\'Good habits are important\'更正式、更有分量</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. Not only ... but also ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>递进关系，展示两个优点/事实</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Not only does exercise improve physical health, but it also boosts mental well-being.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 锻炼不仅能改善身体健康，还能提升心理健康。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 注意：Not only 放句首时，主句要倒装</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. While it is true that ..., ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>先承认对方观点，再转折反驳</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? While it is true that technology saves time, it also creates new pressures.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 虽然技术确实节省了时间，但它也带来了新的压力。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 议论文必备句式，显示思维全面</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. This suggests that ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>引出结论或推断</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Sales increased by 30% last year. This suggests that the strategy is working.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 去年销售额增长了30%。这表明该策略正在奏效。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 比直接说 so 更学术，适合分析类写作</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. In the long run, ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>从长远角度总结</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? In the long run, investing in education benefits the entire society.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 从长远来看，投资教育对整个社会都有益。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 结尾段常用，比 finally 更有深度</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">用以上5个句式各写一句话，主题自定。<br>发在评论区，我来批改！✏️</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：2026年最火英语口头禅</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','写作高分句式：It is essential that / Not only but also / While it is true that / This suggests that / In the long run','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUaKd3cOIr78hIl1MhJqhm-SW1K6KlyAj1pSADby99Ik',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语写作高分句式','英语作文段落没逻辑？这5个句式直接套?','写作分数低，不一定是词汇问题\n很可能是段落句式太单调！\n\n记住这5个，逻辑感立刻上来?\n\n① It is essential that... （强调重要性）\n② Not only... but also... （递进）\n③ While it is true that... （承认+转折）\n④ This suggests that... （引出结论）\n⑤ In the long run... （长远总结）\n\n每个都配了例句，直接背，直接用！\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天写作干货\n\n#英语写作 #写作技巧 #英语学习 #高分句式',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:28:12','2026-03-07 11:43:48',1,NULL),(33,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpX6JUyI4iuVY2QJ-DcYTUrcZdb6ibiIIwCXLmxF3PadI','2026年最火英语口头禅，听懂这5个才算跟上了','Cathy','2026流行英语口头禅：it gives me the ick / no cap / slay / let him cook / understood the assignment','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">每隔一段时间，英语世界都会涌现一批新口头禅。<br>2026年最流行的这5个，你听过几个？</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天整理出来，不只是知道意思，还要知道<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">怎么用、用在哪</strong>。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2026年最火英语口头禅</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套学习资料！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. It gives me the ick</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>让我感到莫名反感/不适</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He chews with his mouth open — it gives me the ick.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他吃东西嘴巴不闭，让我很不舒服。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ick = 恶心感，形容对某人/某事突然失去好感</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. No cap</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>我没在骗你 / 说真的</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? That movie was incredible, no cap.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 那部电影真的太好看了，我没骗你。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ cap = 说谎；no cap = 不吹牛，就是事实</p></section><p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. Slay</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>太厉害了 / 完全征服</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She walked in and absolutely slayed the presentation.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她走进去，那场演讲直接拿捏了。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 原意=杀死，这里是褒义，表示「完全做到了」</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Let him cook</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>让他发挥 / 别打扰他</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Don\'t interrupt — just let him cook.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 别打断，让他发挥就行。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 2024年起流行，来自做饭的隐喻</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. Understood the assignment</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>完全领会了 / 做到位了</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She wore a full Victorian dress to the costume party — understood the assignment.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她穿了完整的维多利亚裙去主题派对——完全领会精髓。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ assignment = 任务；表示把事情做得非常到位</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 用法提示</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">这5个都是口语/社交媒体用语，正式场合不用。<br>但听懂它们，和外国朋友聊天就不会一脸茫然了。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：5个动词，中国人最容易搞混</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','2026流行英语口头禅：it gives me the ick / no cap / slay / let him cook / understood the assignment','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpVoTr_lfDtOh1mtP2wZICBcCbcrj_KyAvzUcVlxeApYF',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','热点英语口语流行词','2026最火英语口头禅?听懂这5个才算跟上了','你知道这些话是什么意思吗？\n\n「It gives me the ick」→ 让我莫名反感\n「No cap」→ 说真的，没骗你\n「Slay」→ 太厉害了，完全拿捏\n「Let him cook」→ 让他发挥，别打扰\n「Understood the assignment」→ 完全领会了\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天英语干货\n\n#英语口语 #流行英语 #英语学习',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:43:48','2026-03-07 11:58:57',1,NULL),(34,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpX6JUyI4iuVY2QJ-DcYTUrcZdb6ibiIIwCXLmxF3PadI','这5个动词，中国人最容易搞混——看完对比例句直接改','Cathy','高频误用动词：borrow/lend tell/say discuss不加about reach不加to rise/raise区别','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语动词用错，往往是因为<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">直接从中文翻译过来</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">下面5个是中国人最常误用的动词，每个都有对比例句，看完直接改。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个高频误用动词，改掉立刻地道</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取口语资料+地道动词搭配手册！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. borrow vs. lend</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>borrow = 我借（向别人借）；lend = 借给（把自己的给别人）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can I borrow your pen? / Can you lend me your pen?</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我能借一下你的笔吗？ / 你能把笔借我吗？</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ Can you borrow me your pen? → 逻辑反了，这句话不通</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. tell vs. say</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>tell = 告诉某人（后接人）；say = 说（不一定有对象）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She told me the truth. / She said she was tired.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她告诉了我实情。 / 她说她累了。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ She told that she was tired. → tell 后面必须先接人</p></section><p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. discuss（不加 about）</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>discuss 本身已含「关于」，后面不加 about</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We discussed the plan for an hour.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们讨论了一个小时的计划。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ We discussed about the plan. → about 多余，去掉</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. reach（不加 to）</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>reach 直接加地点；arrive 才需要 at/in</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We reached the hotel at 9 pm.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们晚上9点到达了酒店。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ We reached to the hotel. → reach 后不加 to</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. rise vs. raise</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>rise = 自己升起（不及物）；raise = 举起/提高（及物，需要宾语）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The sun rises every morning. / Please raise your hand.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 太阳每天升起。 / 请举手。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ Please rise your hand. → raise 才能带宾语</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆方法</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">遇到这5个动词，先问自己：<br>① 动作是自己做还是对别人做？<br>② 后面有没有宾语？<br>想清楚这两点，基本不会再用错。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语作文段落不够有力？5个句式套上去</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','高频误用动词：borrow/lend tell/say discuss不加about reach不加to rise/raise区别','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpfPf-qTZ3HdanMalM_k9r1dO6urG1vfKrzGi5oCvtPVb',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语口语动词搭配','这5个英语动词，中国人99%搞混过❌','❌ Can you borrow me your pen?\n✅ Can you lend me your pen?\n\n❌ She told that she was tired.\n✅ She said she was tired.\n\n❌ We discussed about the plan.\n✅ We discussed the plan.\n\n改掉立刻地道！关注【英语陪跑Go】\n\n#英语口语 #动词搭配 #英语学习',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:43:48','2026-03-07 11:58:57',1,NULL),(35,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpX6JUyI4iuVY2QJ-DcYTUrcZdb6ibiIIwCXLmxF3PadI','英语作文段落不够有力？这5个句式套上去，逻辑感立刻来了','Cathy','写作高分句式：It is essential that / Not only but also / While it is true / This suggests / In the long run','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语作文分数高不高，很大程度看<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">段落内部的逻辑</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">光有连接词不够，还需要这5个句式来撑起论证。每个都配例句，直接套用。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">让段落更有逻辑的5个句式</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作资料+高分句式模板！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. It is + adj. + that ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>强调某件事的性质，开门见山</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? It is essential that students develop good study habits early.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 学生尽早养成良好的学习习惯至关重要。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 比直接说「Good habits are important」更正式、更有分量</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. Not only ... but also ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>递进关系，展示两个优点/事实</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Not only does exercise improve physical health, but it also boosts mental well-being.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 锻炼不仅能改善身体健康，还能提升心理健康。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 注意：Not only 放句首时，主句要倒装</p></section><p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. While it is true that ..., ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>先承认对方观点，再转折反驳</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? While it is true that technology saves time, it also creates new pressures.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 虽然技术确实节省了时间，但它也带来了新的压力。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 议论文必备句式，显示思维全面</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. This suggests that ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>引出结论或推断</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Sales increased by 30% last year. This suggests that the strategy is working.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 去年销售额增长了30%。这表明该策略正在奏效。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 比直接说 so 更学术，适合分析类写作</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. In the long run, ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>从长远角度总结</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? In the long run, investing in education benefits the entire society.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 从长远来看，投资教育对整个社会都有益。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 结尾段常用，比 finally 更有深度</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">用以上5个句式各写一句话，主题自定。<br>发在评论区，我来批改！✏️</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：2026年最火英语口头禅</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','写作高分句式：It is essential that / Not only but also / While it is true / This suggests / In the long run','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpdn4OZXYcbNpTtHHDdZh0f-yLqeMyte7HW1Ob7m_Gl2K',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语写作高分句式','英语作文段落没逻辑？这5个句式直接套?','① It is essential that... （强调重要性）\n② Not only... but also... （递进）\n③ While it is true that... （承认+转折）\n④ This suggests that... （引出结论）\n⑤ In the long run... （长远总结）\n\n每个都配了例句，直接背，直接用！\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天写作干货\n\n#英语写作 #写作技巧 #高分句式',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:43:48','2026-03-07 11:58:57',1,NULL),(36,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYBU_DGh6Kbouoqalx7ioZ4Unhu68Rq7t8emwj2EgIo9','2026年最火英语口头禅，听懂这5个才算跟上了','Cathy','2026流行英语口头禅：it gives me the ick / no cap / slay / let him cook / understood the assignment','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">每隔一段时间，英语世界都会涌现一批新口头禅。<br>2026年最流行的这5个，你听过几个？</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天整理出来，不只是知道意思，还要知道<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">怎么用、用在哪</strong>。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2026年最火英语口头禅</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「资料包」</strong>，获取英语陪跑Go 全套学习资料！</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. It gives me the ick</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>让我感到莫名反感/不适</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He chews with his mouth open — it gives me the ick.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他吃东西嘴巴不闭，让我很不舒服。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ick = 恶心感，形容对某人/某事突然失去好感</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. No cap</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>我没在骗你 / 说真的</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? That movie was incredible, no cap.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 那部电影真的太好看了，我没骗你。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ cap = 说谎；no cap = 不吹牛，就是事实</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. Slay</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>太厉害了 / 完全征服</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She walked in and absolutely slayed the presentation.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她走进去，那场演讲直接拿捏了。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 原意=杀死，这里是褒义，表示「完全做到了」</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Let him cook</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>让他发挥 / 别打扰他</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Don\'t interrupt — just let him cook.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 别打断，让他发挥就行。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 2024年起流行，来自做饭的隐喻</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. Understood the assignment</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>完全领会了 / 做到位了</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She wore a full Victorian dress to the costume party — understood the assignment.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她穿了完整的维多利亚裙去主题派对——完全领会精髓。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ assignment = 任务；表示把事情做得非常到位</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:28px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 用法提示</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">这5个都是口语/社交媒体用语，正式场合不用。<br>但听懂它们，和外国朋友聊天就不会一脸茫然了。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：5个动词，中国人最容易搞混</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','2026流行英语口头禅：it gives me the ick / no cap / slay / let him cook / understood the assignment','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpaof81dp5NWJbObbJWsfzk7zcwY1gkbVDn30EuMJSMnt',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','热点英语口语流行词','2026最火英语口头禅?听懂这5个才算跟上了','你知道这些话是什么意思吗？\n\n「It gives me the ick」→ 让我莫名反感\n「No cap」→ 说真的，没骗你\n「Slay」→ 太厉害了，完全拿捏\n「Let him cook」→ 让他发挥，别打扰\n「Understood the assignment」→ 完全领会了\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天英语干货\n\n#英语口语 #流行英语 #英语学习',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:58:57','2026-03-07 11:59:02',1,NULL),(37,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYBU_DGh6Kbouoqalx7ioZ4Unhu68Rq7t8emwj2EgIo9','这5个动词，中国人最容易搞混——看完对比例句直接改','Cathy','高频误用动词：borrow/lend tell/say discuss不加about reach不加to rise/raise区别','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语动词用错，往往是因为<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">直接从中文翻译过来</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">下面5个是中国人最常误用的动词，每个都有对比例句，看完直接改。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5个高频误用动词，改掉立刻地道</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取口语资料+地道动词搭配手册！</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. borrow vs. lend</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>borrow = 我借（向别人借）；lend = 借给（把自己的给别人）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can I borrow your pen? / Can you lend me your pen?</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我能借一下你的笔吗？ / 你能把笔借我吗？</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ Can you borrow me your pen? → 逻辑反了，这句话不通</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. tell vs. say</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>tell = 告诉某人（后接人）；say = 说（不一定有对象）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She told me the truth. / She said she was tired.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她告诉了我实情。 / 她说她累了。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ She told that she was tired. → tell 后面必须先接人</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. discuss（不加 about）</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>discuss 本身已含「关于」，后面不加 about</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We discussed the plan for an hour.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们讨论了一个小时的计划。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ We discussed about the plan. → about 多余，去掉</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. reach（不加 to）</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>reach 直接加地点；arrive 才需要 at/in</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We reached the hotel at 9 pm.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们晚上9点到达了酒店。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ We reached to the hotel. → reach 后不加 to</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. rise vs. raise</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>rise = 自己升起（不及物）；raise = 举起/提高（及物，需要宾语）</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? The sun rises every morning. / Please raise your hand.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 太阳每天升起。 / 请举手。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ ❌ Please rise your hand. → raise 才能带宾语</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:28px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆方法</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">遇到这5个动词，先问自己：<br>① 动作是自己做还是对别人做？<br>② 后面有没有宾语？<br>想清楚这两点，基本不会再用错。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语作文段落不够有力？5个句式套上去</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','高频误用动词：borrow/lend tell/say discuss不加about reach不加to rise/raise区别','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpVIsrTOFzga5BSioqnXdR6JYcK9uYk4LWe01WWoHLbeC',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语口语动词搭配','这5个英语动词，中国人99%搞混过❌','❌ Can you borrow me your pen?\n✅ Can you lend me your pen?\n\n❌ She told that she was tired.\n✅ She said she was tired.\n\n❌ We discussed about the plan.\n✅ We discussed the plan.\n\n改掉立刻地道！关注【英语陪跑Go】\n\n#英语口语 #动词搭配 #英语学习',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:58:57','2026-03-07 11:59:02',1,NULL),(38,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpYBU_DGh6Kbouoqalx7ioZ4Unhu68Rq7t8emwj2EgIo9','英语作文段落不够有力？这5个句式套上去，逻辑感立刻来了','Cathy','写作高分句式：It is essential that / Not only but also / While it is true / This suggests / In the long run','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语作文分数高不高，很大程度看<strong style=\"color:#4a90e2\">段落内部的逻辑</strong>。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">光有连接词不够，还需要这5个句式来撑起论证。每个都配例句，直接套用。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">让段落更有逻辑的5个句式</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作资料+高分句式模板！</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. It is + adj. + that ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>强调某件事的性质，开门见山</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? It is essential that students develop good study habits early.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 学生尽早养成良好的学习习惯至关重要。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 比直接说「Good habits are important」更正式、更有分量</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. Not only ... but also ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>递进关系，展示两个优点/事实</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Not only does exercise improve physical health, but it also boosts mental well-being.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 锻炼不仅能改善身体健康，还能提升心理健康。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 注意：Not only 放句首时，主句要倒装</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. While it is true that ..., ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>先承认对方观点，再转折反驳</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? While it is true that technology saves time, it also creates new pressures.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 虽然技术确实节省了时间，但它也带来了新的压力。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 议论文必备句式，显示思维全面</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. This suggests that ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>引出结论或推断</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Sales increased by 30% last year. This suggests that the strategy is working.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 去年销售额增长了30%。这表明该策略正在奏效。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 比直接说 so 更学术，适合分析类写作</p></section><section style=\"margin:28px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">5. In the long run, ...</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>意思：</strong>从长远角度总结</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? In the long run, investing in education benefits the entire society.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 从长远来看，投资教育对整个社会都有益。</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e74c3c;margin:4px 0 0\">⚠️ 结尾段常用，比 finally 更有深度</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:28px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 今日打卡任务</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">用以上5个句式各写一句话，主题自定。<br>发在评论区，我来批改！✏️</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，我来回复</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：2026年最火英语口头禅</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','写作高分句式：It is essential that / Not only but also / While it is true / This suggests / In the long run','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpbT4JsxPuh916fujiiMKqOcMOGAnQ-_fCwfir-6OBv4V',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语写作高分句式','英语作文段落没逻辑？这5个句式直接套?','① It is essential that... （强调重要性）\n② Not only... but also... （递进）\n③ While it is true that... （承认+转折）\n④ This suggests that... （引出结论）\n⑤ In the long run... （长远总结）\n\n每个都配了例句，直接背，直接用！\n\n关注【英语陪跑Go】每天写作干货\n\n#英语写作 #写作技巧 #高分句式',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-07 11:58:58','2026-03-07 11:59:02',1,NULL),(39,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUejyvTRnFKsDXjfRcUdhKeqcxxh6uuLduifedGzpHCv','这 5 句中式英语，老外听了当场愣住——你肯定也说过','Cathy','你有没有过这种经历：明明说的每个单词都对，老外却一脸懵？不是他们听力差，是你的英语太「中式」了。今天这 5 个高频错误，90% 的中国人都踩过','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">你有没有过这种经历：明明说的每个单词都对，老外却一脸懵？不是他们听力差，是你的英语太「中式」了。今天这 5 个高频错误，90% 的中国人都踩过，看看你中了几个？</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">Top 1：我想死你了</h2><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「口语」</strong>，获取地道表达合集！</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">❌ 中式：I miss you dead.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>问题：</strong>dead 是形容词，不能这样用</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 地道：I miss you so much!</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>解析：</strong>so much 表示程度，万能搭配</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I miss you so much! It\'s been weeks!</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我超级想你！都好几周了！</p></section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">Top 2：随便你</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">❌ 中式：Whatever.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>问题：</strong>语气很冲，像吵架</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 地道：It\'s up to you.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>解析：</strong>中性表达，把决定权给对方</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Where should we eat? — It\'s up to you.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们去哪吃？— 你定吧。</p></section><p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">Top 3：我给你打电话</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">❌ 中式：I\'ll call your phone.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>问题：</strong>phone 是多余的</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 地道：I\'ll call you.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>解析：</strong>call 后面直接接人</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I\'ll call you later tonight.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我今晚晚点给你打电话。</p></section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">Top 4：这个很适合你</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">❌ 中式：This is very suitable for you.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>问题：</strong>语法没错，但太正式</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 地道：This suits you!</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>解析：</strong>suit 直接作动词，简洁自然</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? That color really suits you!</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 那个颜色真的很适合你！</p></section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">Top 5：我没意见</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">❌ 中式：I have no opinion.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>问题：</strong>听起来像「我不关心」</p></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 地道：I\'m fine with that.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>解析：</strong>表示接受，语气友好</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? How about Friday? — I\'m fine with that.</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 周五怎么样？— 我没问题。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 小贴士</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">这些错误不是语法问题，而是「语用」问题。单词都对，但老外不这么说。多听美剧/播客，慢慢就改掉了。</p></section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">今日打卡</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 小任务</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>选一个</strong>你今天学到的地道表达，在评论区造个句子！</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">别死记硬背。想象一个场景（比如跟朋友约饭），然后用那个场景里的地道表达。这样记得牢，用得出。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：用今天学的表达造个句</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>','你有没有过这种经历：明明说的每个单词都对，老外却一脸懵？不是他们听力差，是你的英语太「中式」了。今天这 5 个高频错误，90% 的中国人都踩过','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpY6a170oiPLwCIuM2HPkqJpNdh_rBzpWADtKfC_o6ejI',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','中式英语趣味纠错','这 5 句中式英语?老外听了当场愣住‼️','每个单词都对，但老外就是听不懂？因为你说的太「中式」了\n\n❌ I miss you dead.\n✅ I miss you so much!\n\n❌ Whatever.\n✅ It\'s up to you.\n\n❌ I\'ll call your phone.\n✅ I\'ll call you.\n\n❌ This is very suitable for you.\n✅ This suits you!\n\n❌ I have no opinion.\n✅ I\'m fine with that.\n\n? 核心：不是语法错，是「老外不这么说」\n\n? 评论区挑战：选一个表达造个句！\n\n#英语口语 #中式英语 #地道英语 #英语学习 #口语提升',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-08 10:40:26','2026-03-08 10:40:36',1,NULL),(40,NULL,'KET 必考！5 组易混词','Cathy',NULL,'<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">KET 考试中，经常会出现拼写相似但意思完全不同的单词。今天这 5 组是 KET 高频考点，必须掌握！</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">每组都配有例句和记忆技巧，看完再也不丢分！</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 1 组：hear vs here</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「KET 易混词」</strong>，获取 100 组 KET 易混词完整清单！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">hear /hɪə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>v. 听见</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can you hear me?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你能听见我说话吗？</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">here /hɪə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>adv. 在这里</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Come here, please.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 请过来这里。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>hear 里有 ear（耳朵），用耳朵听。</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几组词？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','KET 考试中易混词汇讲解：hear vs here, their vs there, buy vs by, week vs weak, feel vs fell',NULL,NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','KET 词汇',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 11:42:36','2026-03-10 11:42:36',1,NULL),(41,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpeiLXe_uthQJTkgvYXEeiHu5Wv7xmWA7BXWTMoXLrO3I','KET 必考！5 组易混词','Cathy','KET 考试中易混词汇讲解：hear vs here, their vs there, buy vs by, week vs weak, feel vs fell','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">KET 考试中，经常会出现拼写相似但意思完全不同的单词。今天这 5 组是 KET 高频考点，必须掌握！</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">每组都配有例句和记忆技巧，看完再也不丢分！</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 1 组：hear vs here</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「KET 易混词」</strong>，获取 100 组 KET 易混词完整清单！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">hear /hɪə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>v. 听见</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can you hear me?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你能听见我说话吗？</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">here /hɪə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>adv. 在这里</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Come here, please.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 请过来这里。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>hear 里有 ear（耳朵），用耳朵听。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 2 组：their vs there vs they\'re</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">their /ðeə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>pron. 他们的</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? This is their house.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这是他们的房子。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">there /ðeə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>adv. 在那里</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Look over there!</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 看那边！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">they\'re /ðeə(r)/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>= they are 他们是</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? They\'re my friends.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他们是我的朋友。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>their 有 heir（继承人）→ 他们的东西；there 有 here→ 地点；they\'re 有撇号 → 缩写。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 3 组：buy vs by vs bye</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">buy /baɪ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>v. 买</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I want to buy a book.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我想买一本书。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">by /baɪ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>prep. 通过；在...旁边</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She sits by the window.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她坐在窗边。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">bye /baɪ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>int. 再见</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Bye! See you tomorrow!</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 再见！明天见！</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>buy 花钱 u（u 像钱包）；by 最短，是介词；bye 有 e = goodbye。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 4 组：week vs weak</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">week /wiːk/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>n. 星期；周</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? There are seven days in a week.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 一周有七天。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">weak /wiːk/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>adj. 弱的；虚弱的</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He is still weak after the illness.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他病后仍然很虚弱。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>week 有两个 e = 七天（多）；weak 有 ea = eat too little（吃得少→虚弱）。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 5 组：feel vs fell</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">feel /fiːl/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>v. 感觉；触摸</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? How do you feel today?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你今天感觉怎么样？</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">fell /fel/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>词性：</strong>v. 跌倒（fall 的过去式）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He fell off the bike yesterday.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他昨天从自行车上摔下来了。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>feel 两个 e = 两只眼睛→用感觉；fell 一个 e = 摔倒了（少了一个）。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 小练习</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选 3 组词各造一个句子，发到评论区，我会逐一批改！</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几组词？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','KET 考试中易混词汇讲解：hear vs here, their vs there, buy vs by, week vs weak, feel vs fell','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpVMbdJoIRrp9zIFZ29Y7IoHYcVKpxTSKbeNP-FPhosgn',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','KET 词汇','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 11:45:44','2026-03-10 11:46:57',1,NULL),(42,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpaGRe63cYrXZHQQRMYBzpM0D-3jIGNeSZWhcngrvh_BL','AI 时代，英语还值得学吗？','Cathy','AI 时代英语学习方法升级，自动化工具辅助学习，30 天学习计划','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最近总有人问我：<strong>\"现在翻译软件这么厉害，AI 也能实时翻译了，英语还值得学吗？\"</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">我的回答很明确：<strong>值得学，但学习方法要升级。</strong></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">AI 能做什么，不能做什么？</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取 AI 英语学习工具清单！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ AI 擅长的：</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:10px 0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>实时翻译（旅游问路、看菜单）</li>\n    <li>语法检查（写作纠错）</li>\n    <li>单词查询（即查即得）</li>\n    <li>发音纠正（口语陪练）</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">❌ AI 做不到的：</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:10px 0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>深度文化交流（理解幽默、梗、潜台词）</li>\n    <li>职场竞争力（外企面试、国际会议）</li>\n    <li>第一手信息获取（英文原版书、学术论文）</li>\n    <li>建立真实连接（和外国人交朋友）</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>翻译软件是拐杖，英语能力是双腿。</strong>拐杖能帮你走一段路，但想走得远、走得稳，还得靠自己的腿。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">我用 AI 工具搭建的英语学习系统</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">作为一个后端工程师，我用自动化工具搭建了一套英语学习系统，每天自动运行，省时省力。</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 场景 1：每日单词自动推送</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">每天早上 8 点，自动推送 10 个 KET/PET 高频词到手机，不用主动打开 App。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 场景 2：听力材料自动收集</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">自动订阅 YouTube 英语学习频道，下载最新视频字幕，提取生词和常用表达。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 场景 3：学习打卡自动提醒</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">设置固定学习时间，提前 10 分钟发送提醒，自动记录学习时长，每周生成进度报告。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 场景 4：阅读素材聚合 + AI 总结</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">RSS 订阅英文新闻，AI 自动总结要点，推送给用户，附带原文链接。</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">30 天 AI 辅助英语学习计划</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.8;margin:0\">\n    <strong>第 1 周：</strong>每天 10 个单词 + 10 分钟听力<br>\n    <strong>第 2 周：</strong>每天 10 个单词 + 15 分钟听力 + 5 分钟口语<br>\n    <strong>第 3 周：</strong>每天 15 个单词 + 20 分钟听力 + 10 分钟口语<br>\n    <strong>第 4 周：</strong>每天 15 个单词 + 20 分钟听力 + 15 分钟阅读\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>关键：</strong>用自动化工具减少\"坚持\"的阻力，让学习变成习惯。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 互动话题</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">你觉得 AI 能替代英语学习吗？评论区聊聊你的看法！</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区聊聊：你用 AI 学英语吗？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','AI 时代英语学习方法升级，自动化工具辅助学习，30 天学习计划','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpfCUep8KNAneLgYOeaHaZjzfD9nIt6Y2PRdnv3oJ6_5K',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','AI 英语学习','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 11:46:23','2026-03-10 11:47:03',1,NULL),(43,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpa5jGYIk7iEfJlFTJ3xgb_YLvXZI-0peB948bwK9tKmL','AI 时代，英语还值得学吗？','Cathy','实测 10 个 AI 英语工具，推荐 3 个真正能提效的：DeepL 翻译、Grammarly 纠错、Speak 口语陪练','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最近总有人问我：<strong>\"现在翻译软件这么厉害，AI 也能实时翻译了，英语还值得学吗？\"</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">我的回答是：<strong>值得学，但要会用工具。</strong> 今天我实测了 10 个 AI 英语工具，选出这 3 个真正能提效的。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">实测 1：翻译工具对比</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取 10 个 AI 英语工具完整清单 + 使用教程！</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">同一段英文，我用 3 个工具翻译，看看效果：</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>原文：</strong>\"The project is behind schedule due to unforeseen circumstances.\"</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? DeepL（推荐）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>翻译：</strong>由于不可预见的情况，项目进度落后了。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">✅ 准确流畅，符合中文表达习惯</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? Google 翻译</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>翻译：</strong>由于不可预见的情况，项目落后于计划。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">✅ 准确但略显生硬</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 百度翻译</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>翻译：</strong>该项目是由于不可预见的情况下落后于时间表。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">⚠️ 能看懂，但\"该项目是由于\"语序不自然</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>结论：</strong>DeepL 最自然，适合正式文档；Google 翻译免费够用；百度翻译中文语境更好。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">实测 2：语法检查工具</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">我故意写了一个有语法错误的句子，看看 AI 能不能发现：</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>错误句子：</strong>\"She don\'t like to eat apples because they is too sweet.\"</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? Grammarly（推荐）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>纠错：</strong>don\'t → doesn\'t / is → are</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">✅ 两个错误都发现，还解释了主谓一致规则</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\"><strong>费用：</strong>免费版够用，高级版$12/月（学生 8 折）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? Wordtune</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>纠错：</strong>发现错误，并提供 3 种改写建议</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">✅ 不仅能纠错，还能优化表达</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\"><strong>费用：</strong>免费版每日 10 次，高级版$10/月</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>结论：</strong>Grammarly 最适合学习，解释详细；Wordtune 适合写作优化。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">实测 3：口语陪练工具</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">口语是 AI 最能帮上忙的领域，我试了 3 个能对话的 AI：</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? Speak（推荐）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>特点：</strong>AI 情景对话，实时纠正发音</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">✅ 场景丰富（点餐/面试/旅行），反馈及时</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\"><strong>费用：</strong>免费试用 7 天，$12/月</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 英语流利说</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>特点：</strong>AI 打分 + 真人课程</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">✅ 发音评分准确，课程体系完整</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\"><strong>费用：</strong>基础免费，进阶课程¥99/月</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? ChatGPT 语音</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>特点：</strong>自由对话，话题无限</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">⚠️ 能对话，但不纠正发音，适合进阶练习</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\"><strong>费用：</strong>Plus 版$20/月</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>结论：</strong>初学者用 Speak，体系化学习；进阶用 ChatGPT，自由对话。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">最终结论</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 我的推荐组合</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    <strong>初学者：</strong>DeepL（翻译）+ Grammarly（纠错）+ Speak（口语）<br>\n    <strong>进阶者：</strong>Google 翻译（免费）+ Wordtune（写作）+ ChatGPT（对话）\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>AI 不是替代你学英语，而是帮你学得更快。</strong>工具再好，也得你开口说、动手写。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 福利领取</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取：<br>\n  1. 10 个 AI 英语工具完整清单<br>\n  2. 每个工具的详细使用教程<br>\n  3. 30 天 AI 辅助学习计划表</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区聊聊：你用哪个 AI 工具学英语？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','实测 10 个 AI 英语工具，推荐 3 个真正能提效的：DeepL 翻译、Grammarly 纠错、Speak 口语陪练','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpeb3zw6W8n-w33RgGmWkVWnbDplhrFCDZwkfxnu4MTuZ',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','AI 英语学习','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 11:53:03','2026-03-10 11:53:06',1,NULL),(44,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpQSTFEvGa0BqRlRJoN2hbL5QIxt20DJVfO-sRj23nQEU','OpenClaw 火了，但 90% 的人装完就扔：AI 工具的大跃进陷阱','Cathy','OpenClaw 很火，但很多人装了不知道干嘛。AI 工具不是能力，踏实学习才是正道。30 天计划帮你达成目标。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最近 OpenClaw 很火，GitHub Star 暴涨，群里每天都有人问：\"装好了，然后呢？\"</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">这个问题，像极了 50 年代的大跃进——<strong>工具到位了，能力没跟上。</strong></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">AI 工具的 3 个幻觉</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取 30 天 AI 辅助学习计划表！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">幻觉 1：\"装了就会了\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">收藏了 10 个 AI 工具，但从来没打开过。工具≠能力，就像买了跑步机不等于瘦了。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">幻觉 2：\"免费的最好\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">花 3 小时找免费教程，却不愿意花 30 分钟系统学习。时间成本最高，但你感觉\"没花钱\"。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">幻觉 3：\"等准备好了再学\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">对比了 20 个工具，看了 50 篇评测，最后说\"我再研究研究\"。永远准备不好，直接开始才是正解。</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">英语学习的真相</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">AI 工具能帮你什么？不能帮你什么？说点实在的。</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ DeepL 能帮你翻译邮件</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">但帮不了你和老外谈生意</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\">场景：写邮件 10 分钟搞定 ✅ 开会谈判 ❌</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ Grammarly 能帮你纠错</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">但帮不了你写创意文案</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\">场景：语法检查 ✅ 写出打动人心的文案 ❌</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ Speak 能陪你练对话</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">但帮不了你理解文化梗</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\">场景：日常对话 ✅ 听懂幽默和潜台词 ❌</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>工具是杠杆，但支点是你自己。</strong>没有支点，杠杆再长也撬不动东西。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">正确的打开方式</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">别学大跃进，踏踏实实来。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">第 1 步：先定目标（10 分钟）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">3 个月后，你要达成什么？<br>\n  ✅ 能写工作邮件<br>\n  ✅ 能看懂英文文档<br>\n  ✅ 能和老外简单交流<br>\n  ❌ \"学好英语\"（太模糊，无效）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">第 2 步：只选 1-2 个工具（30 分钟）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">别贪多，选最匹配的：<br>\n  • 写邮件 → DeepL + Grammarly<br>\n  • 练口语 → Speak<br>\n  • 备考 KET/PET → 每日英语听力 + 扇贝单词</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">第 3 步：每天 15 分钟，坚持 30 天</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">• 第 1 周：熟悉工具，每天翻译 1 篇短文<br>\n  • 第 2 周：用工具写 3 封邮件<br>\n  • 第 3 周：每天对话练习 10 分钟<br>\n  • 第 4 周：综合实战（模拟面试/演讲）</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">两个学习者的对比</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 学习者 A（大跃进式）</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>收藏 10 个 AI 工具</li>\n    <li>每天刷工具评测</li>\n    <li>3 个月后：\"哪个工具最好？\"</li>\n    <li>结果：原地踏步</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 学习者 B（踏实式）</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>只用 DeepL + Grammarly</li>\n    <li>每天翻译 1 篇短文 + 写 1 封邮件</li>\n    <li>3 个月后：\"能独立写工作邮件了\"</li>\n    <li>结果：达成目标</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>装 100 个工具，不如把 1 个工具用 100 次。</strong></p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 福利领取</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取：<br>\n  1. 30 天 AI 辅助学习计划表（可直接套用）<br>\n  2. 5 个精选工具清单（避免踩坑）<br>\n  3. 学习打卡模板（坚持 30 天）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 核心金句</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    • OpenClaw 很火，但火的是工具，不是你<br>\n    • AI 能帮你翻译邮件，但帮不了你和老外谈生意<br>\n    • 这不是 AI 革命，这是\"收藏即学会\"的自我安慰<br>\n    • 大跃进式的学英语，结局就是大跃退\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区聊聊：你中了几个幻觉？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','OpenClaw 很火，但很多人装了不知道干嘛。AI 工具不是能力，踏实学习才是正道。30 天计划帮你达成目标。','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpRhXJX0Yu3zPJ9Cnlc4rjHivWdtLhFZdtMDTmilU6Eo7',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','AI 英语学习','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 12:00:26','2026-03-10 12:00:29',1,NULL),(45,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpaiZrA5N6Dm0KiS2gpaI_kgpbre4YW4hei43EsjoWAyJ','KET 必考！8 组高频易混词（错误率 90%）','Cathy','KET 考试 8 组高频易混词：say/tell/speak/talk, look/see/watch/read, bring/take/fetch/carry, borrow/lend/keep, arrive/reach/get to','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">KET 考试中，这 8 组易混词错误率最高！今天一次性讲清楚，看完再也不丢分。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 1 组：say vs tell vs speak vs talk</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「KET 易混词」</strong>，获取 50 组 KET 易混词完整 PDF！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">say /seɪ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>强调说话内容，后接说的话</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He said \"Hello\" to me.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他跟我说了\"你好\"。（强调说的内容）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">tell /tel/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>强调告诉某人，必须接人作宾语</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She told me the news.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她告诉了我这个消息。（tell + 人 + 事）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">speak /spiːk/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>强调说话能力或正式发言</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can you speak English?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你会说英语吗？（强调语言能力）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">talk /tɔːk/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>强调交谈、聊天</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? They talked for hours.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他们聊了好几个小时。（强调交流过程）</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆口诀：</strong>say 内容 tell 人，speak 能力 talk 聊天。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 2 组：look vs see vs watch vs read</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">look /lʊk/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>有意识地看，强调动作，常接 at</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Look at the blackboard!</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 看黑板！（主动去看）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">see /siː/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>看见，强调结果，无意识看到</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I saw a bird in the tree.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我看见树上有只鸟。（无意中看到）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">watch /wɒtʃ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>观看移动的事物（电视、比赛等）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We watched a football match.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们看了一场足球赛。（观看移动物体）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">read /riːd/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>阅读文字材料（书、报、杂志）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She is reading a book.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她正在看书。（阅读文字）</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆口诀：</strong>look 主动 see 结果，watch 移动 read 文字。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 3 组：bring vs take vs fetch vs carry</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">bring /brɪŋ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>带来（从别处到说话人这里）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Please bring your homework tomorrow.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 明天请把你的作业带来。（带到说话人这里）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">take /teɪk/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>带走（从说话人这里到别处）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Take this book to the library.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 把这本书带到图书馆去。（从说话人这里带走）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">fetch /fetʃ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>去取来（去某处拿东西再回来）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Go and fetch some water.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 去取些水来。（去 + 回）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">carry /ˈkæri/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>搬运、携带（无方向性）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She carried a heavy bag.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她提着一个沉重的包。（强调负重）</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆口诀：</strong>bring 来 take 去，fetch 去取 carry 提。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 4 组：borrow vs lend vs keep</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">borrow /ˈbɒrəʊ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>借入（从别人那里借），常接 from</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can I borrow your pen?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我能借你的钢笔吗？（我借入）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">lend /lend/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>借出（借给别人），常接 to</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? Can you lend me some money?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你能借我一些钱吗？（你借出）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">keep /kiːp/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>保存、保留（强调持续时间）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? How long can I keep the book?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这本书我可以保存多久？（强调时长）</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆口诀：</strong>borrow 借入 lend 借出，keep 强调保存时长。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 5 组：arrive vs reach vs get to</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">arrive /əˈraɪv/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>到达（不及物动词），大地点用 at，小地点用 in</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We arrived in Beijing yesterday.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们昨天到达北京。（大地点用 in）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">reach /riːtʃ/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>到达（及物动词），直接接地点</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? We reached the station at 9.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们 9 点到达车站。（直接接地点）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get to</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>到达（口语常用），接地点</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? What time did you get to school?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你几点到学校的？（口语化）</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆口诀：</strong>arrive 不及物，reach 直接接，get to 最口语。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 课后练习</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">用正确的词填空：<br>\n  1. Can you ___ me your dictionary? (borrow/lend)<br>\n  2. I ___ home at 6 PM yesterday. (arrived/reached/got to)<br>\n  3. Please ___ your homework tomorrow. (bring/take)<br>\n  4. Don\'t ___ at others. (look/see/watch)<br>\n  5. She ___ a novel every night. (reads/watches)</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 福利领取</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">回复关键词<strong>「KET 易混词」</strong>，获取：<br>\n  1. 50 组 KET 易混词完整 PDF<br>\n  2. 配套练习题 + 答案<br>\n  3. 记忆音频（磨耳朵用）</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几组词？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','KET 考试 8 组高频易混词：say/tell/speak/talk, look/see/watch/read, bring/take/fetch/carry, borrow/lend/keep, arrive/reach/get to','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpRZKMRBCEF1q19FlwO5TDP0bfhe3vdfSuHHv15-fEtnb',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','KET 词汇','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 13:32:21','2026-03-10 13:32:24',1,NULL),(46,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSziOc6X8cfL9rtbdLHlA1v4qYGLAwvAY1-goCReAZn5','OpenClaw 火了，但 90% 的人装完就扔：AI 工具的大跃进陷阱','Cathy','OpenClaw 很火，但很多人装了不知道干嘛。AI 工具不是能力，踏实学习才是正道。30 天计划帮你达成目标。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最近 OpenClaw 很火，GitHub Star 暴涨，群里每天都有人问：\"装好了，然后呢？\"</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">这个问题，像极了 50 年代的大跃进——<strong>工具到位了，能力没跟上。</strong></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">AI 工具的 3 个幻觉</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取 30 天 AI 辅助学习计划表！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">幻觉 1：\"装了就会了\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">收藏了 10 个 AI 工具，但从来没打开过。工具≠能力，就像买了跑步机不等于瘦了。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">幻觉 2：\"免费的最好\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">花 3 小时找免费教程，却不愿意花 30 分钟系统学习。时间成本最高，但你感觉\"没花钱\"。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">幻觉 3：\"等准备好了再学\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\">对比了 20 个工具，看了 50 篇评测，最后说\"我再研究研究\"。永远准备不好，直接开始才是正解。</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">英语学习的真相</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">AI 工具能帮你什么？不能帮你什么？说点实在的。</p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ DeepL 能帮你翻译邮件</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">但帮不了你和老外谈生意</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\">场景：写邮件 10 分钟搞定 ✅ 开会谈判 ❌</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ Grammarly 能帮你纠错</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">但帮不了你写创意文案</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\">场景：语法检查 ✅ 写出打动人心的文案 ❌</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ Speak 能陪你练对话</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\">但帮不了你理解文化梗</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#888;margin:8px 0 0\">场景：日常对话 ✅ 听懂幽默和潜台词 ❌</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>工具是杠杆，但支点是你自己。没有支点，杠杆再长也撬不动东西。</strong></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">正确的打开方式</h2>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">别学大跃进，踏踏实实来。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">第 1 步：先定目标（10 分钟）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">3 个月后，你要达成什么？<br>\n  ✅ 能写工作邮件<br>\n  ✅ 能看懂英文文档<br>\n  ✅ 能和老外简单交流<br>\n  ❌ \"学好英语\"（太模糊，无效）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">第 2 步：只选 1-2 个工具（30 分钟）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">别贪多，选最匹配的：<br>\n  • 写邮件 → DeepL + Grammarly<br>\n  • 练口语 → Speak<br>\n  • 备考 KET/PET → 每日英语听力 + 扇贝单词</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">第 3 步：每天 15 分钟，坚持 30 天</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">• 第 1 周：熟悉工具，每天翻译 1 篇短文<br>\n  • 第 2 周：用工具写 3 封邮件<br>\n  • 第 3 周：每天对话练习 10 分钟<br>\n  • 第 4 周：综合实战（模拟面试/演讲）</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">两个学习者的对比</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 学习者 A（大跃进式）</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>收藏 10 个 AI 工具</li>\n    <li>每天刷工具评测</li>\n    <li>3 个月后：\"哪个工具最好？\"</li>\n    <li>结果：原地踏步</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">? 学习者 B（踏实式）</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>只用 DeepL + Grammarly</li>\n    <li>每天翻译 1 篇短文 + 写 1 封邮件</li>\n    <li>3 个月后：\"能独立写工作邮件了\"</li>\n    <li>结果：达成目标</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong>装 100 个工具，不如把 1 个工具用 100 次。</strong></p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 核心金句</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>OpenClaw 很火，但火的是工具，不是你</li>\n    <li>AI 能帮你翻译邮件，但帮不了你和老外谈生意</li>\n    <li>这不是 AI 革命，这是\"收藏即学会\"的自我安慰</li>\n    <li>大跃进式的学英语，结局就是大跃退</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 福利领取</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">回复关键词<strong>「AI 英语」</strong>，获取：<br>\n  1. 30 天 AI 辅助学习计划表（可直接套用）<br>\n  2. 5 个精选工具清单（避免踩坑）<br>\n  3. 学习打卡模板（坚持 30 天）</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区聊聊：你中了几个幻觉？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','OpenClaw 很火，但很多人装了不知道干嘛。AI 工具不是能力，踏实学习才是正道。30 天计划帮你达成目标。','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSo-MLKxwS-P9hCQaa-eFotE2gYaZElJprEfASjHeBHM',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','AI 英语学习','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-10 13:33:23','2026-03-10 13:33:26',1,NULL),(47,NULL,'【FCE备考】FCE 必备短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have | 技巧','英语陪跑go','“I used to play football, but now I don’t.” — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；“She should have told me earlier.” — 语法精准，B2级表达力跃然纸上；“You need','<section><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:#3a3a3a;margin:10px 0;\">“I <strong>used to</strong> play football, but now I don’t.” — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；<br>“She <strong>should have told</strong> me earlier.” — 语法精准，B2级表达力跃然纸上；<br>“You <strong>needn’t have waited</strong> — the meeting was cancelled!” — 这一句，直接让考官在写作Part 2里给你加半分！<br>但现实是：FCE考生中，近68%在Paper 2 Writing和Paper 4 Speaking Part 3中，因这三个结构误用丢分——不是不会，而是“似懂非懂”：used to 写成 use to；should have 后接动词原形；needn’t have 后加 to do… 考场3秒犹豫，就是0.5分的差距。</p></section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? 核心策略：三把钥匙，打开B2级时态与情态逻辑之门</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? used to + 动词原形</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">表示过去**长期、习惯性**的动作或状态，且现在已完全停止（隐含对比）。否定式为 <em>didn’t use to</em>（注意：not 后是 <strong>use</strong>，非 used）；疑问式为 <em>Did you use to…?</em></p>\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>He used to played guitar.</em> — “used to”后必须接动词原形，不可加-ed</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>He used to play guitar.</em> — 正确！强调“他过去常弹，现在不弹了”</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? should have + 过去分词</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">表达对**过去未发生之事的遗憾、责备或建议**（本该做却没做）。主语可为第一/二/三人称；常与 <em>by now / last week / yesterday</em> 等明确过去时间状语呼应。</p>\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>You should have to call her.</em> — “should have”后不可再加情态动词或to</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>You should have called her.</em> — 正确！暗含“你没打，现在后悔了”</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? needn’t have + 过去分词</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">表示“过去做了某事，但其实**没必要**”——动作已发生，结果却多余。语气常带轻微无奈或幽默感，是B2级高分标志之一。</p>\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>We needn’t have bought so much food.</em> — 错在 needn’t have 的第三人称单数形式错误（应为 needn’t have，无-s）</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>We needn’t have bought so much food.</em> — 正确！强调“我们买了，但其实不用买这么多”</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? 对比辨析：used to vs. would</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">两者都表“过去常常”，但 <em>would</em> **仅用于重复性动作**（不可用于状态），且**不能用于否定句/疑问句**；<em>used to</em> 动作+状态皆可，且有完整否定与疑问形式。</p>\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>Did she would go there every summer?</em> — “would”不可用于疑问句</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>Did she use to go there every summer?</em> — 正确！</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? 情态逻辑链：should have → could have → might have</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">三者均表“过去可能性”，但程度递减：<br><strong>should have</strong> = 强烈责任/预期（大概率该做）<br><strong>could have</strong> = 能力上可行（但未必该做）<br><strong>might have</strong> = 不确定性最高（可能做了，也可能没做）</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? Speaking Part 3 高光表达</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">在讨论“教育方式变化”“科技影响生活”等话题时，自然嵌入：<br>• <em>Students used to memorise facts by heart — now they search online.</em><br>• <em>Teachers should have received more digital training before remote learning started.</em><br>• <em>We needn’t have printed all those handouts — the PDF worked perfectly!</em></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px','“I used to play football, but now I don’t.” — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；“She should have told me earlier.” — 语法精准，B2级表达力跃然纸上；“You needn’t have waited — the meeting was cancelled!” — 这一句，直接让考官在写作Part 2里给你加半分！但现实是：FCE考生中，近68%在Paper 2 Writing和Paper 4 Speaking Part 3中，因这三个结构误用丢分——不是不会，而是“似懂非懂”：used to 写成 use to；should have 后接动词原形；needn’t have 后加 to do… 考场3秒犹豫，就是0.5分的差距。\n\n? 核心策略：三把钥匙，打开B2级时态与情态逻辑之门\n\n\n? used to + 动词原形\n表示过去**长期、习惯性**的动作或状态，且现在已完全停止（隐含对比）。否定式为 didn’t use to（注意：not 后是 use，非 used）；疑问式为 Did you use to…?\n\n❌ He used to played guitar. — “used to”后必须接动词原形，不可加-ed\n✅ He used to play guitar. — 正确！强调“他过去常弹，现在不弹了”\n\n\n\n\n? should have + 过去分词\n表达对**过去未发生之事的遗憾、责备或建议**（本该做却没做）。主语可为第一/二/三人称；常与 by now / last week / yesterday 等明确过去时间状语呼应。\n\n❌ You should have to call her. — “should have”后不可再加情态动词或to\n✅ You should have called her. — 正确！暗含“你没打，现在后悔了”\n\n\n\n\n? needn’t have + 过去分词\n表示“过去做了某事，但其实**没必要**”——动作已发生，结果却多余。语气常带轻微无奈或幽默感，是B2级高分标志之一。\n\n❌ We needn’t have bought so much food. — 错在 needn’t have 的第三人称单数形式错误（应为 needn’t have，无-s）\n✅ We needn’t have bought so much food. — 正确！强调“我们买了，但其实不用买这么多”\n\n\n\n\n? 对比辨析：used to vs. would\n两者都表“过去常常”，但 would **仅用于重复性动作**（不可用于状态），且**不能用于否定句/疑问句**；used to 动作+状态皆可，且有完整否定与疑问形式。\n\n❌ Did she would go there every summer? — “would”不可用于疑问句\n✅ Did she use to go there every summer? — 正确！\n\n\n\n\n? 情态逻辑链：should have → could have → might have\n三者均表“过去可能性”，但程度递减：should have = 强烈责任/预期（大概率该做）could have = 能力上可行（但未必该做）might have = 不确定性最高（可能做了，也可能没做）\n\n\n\n? Speaking Part 3 高光表达\n在讨论“教育方式变化”“科技影响生活”等话题时，自然嵌入：• Students used to memorise facts by heart — now they search online.• Teachers should have received more digital training before remote learning started.• We needn’t have printed all those handouts — the PDF worked perfectly!\n\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpRVL72lgTFD5ivnjjFzC7QbWKzxN-mXHH4YhjyUt8W4J',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_fce_干货','fce FCE 必备短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-11 09:16:10','2026-03-11 09:16:10',1,NULL),(48,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSn78xMd7syLpN6mrqLXuEz30Aft3thI5YPmQPIKPvVv','【FCE备考】FCE 必备短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have | 技巧','英语陪跑go','“I used to play piano when I was ten.” — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；“She should have told me earlier.” — 语法精准，B2级逻辑跃然纸上；“You needn’t ha','<section><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:#3a3a3a;margin:10px 0;\">“I <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">used to</strong> play piano when I was ten.” — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；<br>“She <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">should have told</strong> me earlier.” — 语法精准，B2级逻辑跃然纸上；<br>“You <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">needn’t have waited</strong> — I arrived on time!” — 这一句，直接拉开与A2/B1考生的差距。<br>但考场真实一幕是：一位FCE考生在Writing Part 1（邮件）中写道：<em>I should have known that before</em> ✅，下一行却写：<em>I needn’t to wait</em> ❌——瞬间扣掉语法分。短语不是“背下来就行”，而是“用对语境、用准时态、用活情态”。今天，我们彻底拆解FCE三大高频易错短语：used to / should have / needn’t have。</p></section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? used to：过去习惯 ≠ 一般过去时</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? used to：专指“过去长期、重复、现已终止的习惯或状态”</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">✅ <em>I used to live in Shanghai</em> — 强调“现在不住了”；<br>✅ <em>He used to smoke, but he quit in 2020</em> — 习惯+明确终止；<br>❌ <em>I used to go to the park last weekend</em> — 错！last weekend 是单次具体时间，用一般过去时：<em>I went to the park last weekend</em>。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? should have：后悔的“本该”</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? should have + 过去分词：表达对过去事实的责备、遗憾或合理推测</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">✅ <em>You should have checked the weather forecast</em> — 暗示“结果淋雨了”；<br>✅ <em>She shouldn’t have said that in front of her boss</em> — 含道德/社交判断；<br>⚠️ 注意：不表示“实际发生”，只表达主观评价。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? needn’t have：做了不必做的事</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? needn’t have + 过去分词：强调“某事已做，但事后证明没必要”</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">✅ <em>You needn’t have bought so many snacks — we ordered pizza!</em> — 已买，但多余；<br>✅ <em>He needn’t have worried; everything went smoothly</em> — 已担心，实则无须；<br>❌ <em>She needn’t have studied hard because she passed</em> — 不严谨！passing ≠ proof of no need → 更自然：<em>She needn’t have studied so hard; she passed easily</em>。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? 三者核心对比：一张表看本质</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>I should have gone to bed early yesterday</em> — 若没去，只是后悔；但若“去了却还是熬夜”，就混淆了事实与评价</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>I should have gone to bed early — I’m exhausted today</em> — 后果清晰，逻辑闭环</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>They used to be married since 2010</em> — “since”搭配现在完成时，与used to冲突</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>They used to be married; they divorced in 2020</em> — 状态终止，时间明确</p>\n</section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? 例题剖析：FCE Writing Part 1 邮件真题</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #28a745;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#28a745;margin:0 0 12px;\">✅ 写作片段 & 评分依据</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">“Thanks for your help with the project! I <em>should have asked you sooner</em> — my notes were incomplete. And don’t worry about the presentation tomorrow: you <em>needn’t have prepared extra slides</em>, as the teacher said we’ll only show our main findings. By the way, I <em>used to work</em> at that café near school — it’s still open!”<br>? <strong>Grammar (5/5)</strong>：三个结构全部正确，时态逻辑严密；<br>? <strong>Discourse (4/5)</strong>：自然衔接，口语化但得体；<br>? <strong>Lexical Resource (4/5)</strong>：avoid repetition (asked / prepared / worked) — 高分关键。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? 提升路径：从“认得”到“脱口而出”</p></section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;margin:0 0 12px;\">⚠️ 分阶段训练建议</p>\n<ul style=\"margin:10px 0;padding-left:20px;\">\n<li style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2.0;margin:6px 0;\">? <strong>第1周（识别）</strong>：精读3篇FCE Reading Part 5，圈出所有 used to / should have','“I used to play piano when I was ten.” — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；“She should have told me earlier.” — 语法精准，B2级逻辑跃然纸上；“You needn’t have waited — I arrived on time!” — 这一句，直接拉开与A2/B1考生的差距。但考场真实一幕是：一位FCE考生在Writing Part 1（邮件）中写道：I should have known that before ✅，下一行却写：I needn’t to wait ❌——瞬间扣掉语法分。短语不是“背下来就行”，而是“用对语境、用准时态、用活情态”。今天，我们彻底拆解FCE三大高频易错短语：used to / should have / needn’t have。\n\n? used to：过去习惯 ≠ 一般过去时\n\n\n? used to：专指“过去长期、重复、现已终止的习惯或状态”\n✅ I used to live in Shanghai — 强调“现在不住了”；✅ He used to smoke, but he quit in 2020 — 习惯+明确终止；❌ I used to go to the park last weekend — 错！last weekend 是单次具体时间，用一般过去时：I went to the park last weekend。\n\n\n? should have：后悔的“本该”\n\n\n? should have + 过去分词：表达对过去事实的责备、遗憾或合理推测\n✅ You should have checked the weather forecast — 暗示“结果淋雨了”；✅ She shouldn’t have said that in front of her boss — 含道德/社交判断；⚠️ 注意：不表示“实际发生”，只表达主观评价。\n\n\n? needn’t have：做了不必做的事\n\n\n? needn’t have + 过去分词：强调“某事已做，但事后证明没必要”\n✅ You needn’t have bought so many snacks — we ordered pizza! — 已买，但多余；✅ He needn’t have worried; everything went smoothly — 已担心，实则无须；❌ She needn’t have studied hard because she passed — 不严谨！passing ≠ proof of no need → 更自然：She needn’t have studied so hard; she passed easily。\n\n\n? 三者核心对比：一张表看本质\n\n\n❌ I should have gone to bed early yesterday — 若没去，只是后悔；但若“去了却还是熬夜”，就混淆了事实与评价\n✅ I should have gone to bed early — I’m exhausted today — 后果清晰，逻辑闭环\n\n\n\n❌ They used to be married since 2010 — “since”搭配现在完成时，与used to冲突\n✅ They used to be married; they divorced in 2020 — 状态终止，时间明确\n\n\n? 例题剖析：FCE Writing Part 1 邮件真题\n\n\n✅ 写作片段 & 评分依据\n“Thanks for your help with the project! I should have asked you sooner — my notes were incomplete. And don’t worry about the presentation tomorrow: you needn’t have prepared extra slides, as the teacher said we’ll only show our main findings. By the way, I used to work at that café near school — it’s still open!”? Grammar (5/5)：三个结构全部正确，时态逻辑严密；? Discourse (4/5)：自然衔接，口语化但得体；? Lexical Resource (4/5)：avoid repetition (asked / prepared / worked) — 高分关键。\n\n\n? 提升路径：从“认得”到“脱口而出”\n\n\n⚠️ 分阶段训练建议\n\n? 第1周（识别）：精读3篇FCE Reading Part 5，圈出所有 used to / should have','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpbFqSZe3KftTQE8qWVTqThlSFD72qRQ76yo3q6B66beq',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_fce_干货','FCE 短语 语法 备考',NULL,NULL,4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-11 09:17:11','2026-03-11 09:23:54',1,NULL),(49,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpdKENpb0_nicDrxMPy2eDmDEgs-e2xU2HoZ9EBdIANWa','【FCE 备考】FCE 必备短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have | 技巧','英语陪跑 go','FCE 必备短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have — 考场真实错误案例 + 核心用法解析 + 真题评分标准','<section><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:#3a3a3a;margin:10px 0;\">\"I <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">used to</strong> play piano when I was ten.\" — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；<br>\"She <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">should have told</strong> me earlier.\" — 语法精准，B2 级逻辑跃然纸上；<br>\"You <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">needn\'t have waited</strong> — I arrived on time!\" — 这一句，直接拉开与 A2/B1 考生的差距。</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:#3a3a3a;margin:10px 0;\">但考场真实一幕是：一位 FCE 考生在 Writing Part 1（邮件）中写道：<em>I should have known that before</em> ✅，下一行却写：<em>I needn\'t to wait</em> ❌——瞬间扣掉语法分。</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:#3a3a3a;margin:10px 0;\">短语不是\"背下来就行\"，而是\"用对语境、用准时态、用活情态\"。今天，我们彻底拆解 FCE 三大高频易错短语：<strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">used to</strong> / <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">should have</strong> / <strong style=\"color:#e8641a;\">needn\'t have</strong>。</p></section><section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? used to：过去习惯 ≠ 一般过去时</p></section><section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? used to：专指\"过去长期、重复、现已终止的习惯或状态\"</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">✅ <em>I used to live in Shanghai</em> — 强调\"现在不住了\"；<br>✅ <em>He used to smoke, but he quit in 2020</em> — 习惯 + 明确终止；<br>❌ <em>I used to go to the park last weekend</em> — 错！last weekend 是单次具体时间，用一般过去时：<em>I went to the park last weekend</em>。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>I used to watch a movie yesterday</em> — 错！yesterday 是单次过去时间</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>I watched a movie yesterday</em> — 一般过去时，描述单次动作</p></section><section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? should have：后悔的\"本该\"</p></section><section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? should have + 过去分词：表达对过去事实的责备、遗憾或合理推测</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">✅ <em>You should have checked the weather forecast</em> — 暗示\"结果淋雨了\"；<br>✅ <em>She shouldn\'t have said that in front of her boss</em> — 含道德/社交判断；<br>⚠️ 注意：不表示\"实际发生\"，只表达主观评价。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>I should have went to bed early</em> — 错！went 是过去式，应该用过去分词 gone</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>I should have gone to bed early</em> — should have + 过去分词</p></section><section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? needn\'t have：做了不必做的事</p></section><section style=\"background:#e8f4fd;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 12px;\">? needn\'t have + 过去分词：强调\"某事已做，但事后证明没必要\"</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">✅ <em>You needn\'t have bought so many snacks — we ordered pizza!</em> — 已买，但多余；<br>✅ <em>He needn\'t have worried; everything went smoothly</em> — 已担心，实则无须；<br>❌ <em>She needn\'t have studied hard because she passed</em> — 不严谨！passing ≠ proof of no need → 更自然：<em>She needn\'t have studied so hard; she passed easily</em>。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#e74c3c;\">❌ <em>You needn\'t to wait</em> — 错！needn\'t 后直接加动词原形，或者用 needn\'t have done</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#28a745;\">✅ <em>You needn\'t wait</em> — 现在不必等<br>✅ <em>You needn\'t have waited</em> — 当时不必等（但等了）</p></section><section><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;margin:20px 0 10px;\">? 例题剖析：FCE Writing Part 1 邮件真题</p></section><section style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0;border-left:4px solid #28a745;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#28a745;margin:0 0 12px;\">✅ 写作片段 &amp; 评分依据</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">\"Thanks for your help with the project! I <em>should have asked you sooner</em> — my notes were incomplete. And don\'t worry about the presentation tomorrow: you <em>needn\'t have prepared extra slides</em>, as the teacher said we\'ll only show our main findings. By the way, I <em>used to work</em> at that café near school — it\'s still open!\"</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0;\">? <strong>Grammar (5/5)</strong>：三个结构全部正确，时态逻辑严密；<br>? <strong>Discourse (4/5)</strong>：自然衔接，口语化但得体；<br>? <strong>Lexical Resource (4/5)</strong>：avoid repetition (asked / prepared / worked) — 高分关键。</p></section><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:30px 0;padding:20px;background:#f5f5f5;border-radius:10px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#6a6a6a;\">觉得有用？转发给需要的家长 ?</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;\">关注<strong>英语陪跑 Go</strong>，每天一点，备考不焦虑。</p></section>','FCE 必备短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have — 考场真实错误案例 + 核心用法解析 + 真题评分标准','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpTOc_XM0x1z4XTMzYFNShu6ekCpD_wMoVK2bD8qe4hO7',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_fce_干货','FCE 短语 语法 备考','','',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-11 09:25:03','2026-03-11 11:52:18',1,NULL),(50,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpWMFqWmxZCHi_snPGrBuILwaDQp6rkODRuqWVQhAz1K7','FCE 必考！3 大高频易错短语（错误率 85%）','英语陪跑 go','FCE 写作高频易错短语：used to/should have/needn\'t have，90% 的考生都混淆过！今天彻底搞懂这 3 组 B2 级核心短语，附真题评分标准。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\"I used to play piano when I was ten.\" — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；\"She should have told me earlier.\" — 语法精准，B2 级逻辑跃然纸上；\"You needn\'t have waited — I arrived on time!\" — 这一句，直接拉开与 A2/B1 考生的差距。</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">但考场真实一幕是：一位 FCE 考生在 Writing Part 1（邮件）中写道：I should have known that before ✅，下一行却写：I needn\'t to wait ❌——瞬间扣掉语法分。</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天这 3 个 FCE 高频易错短语，必须掌握！每组都配有真题例句和评分标准，看完再也不丢分！</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「FCE 短语」</strong>，获取 50 组 FCE 必备短语完整清单！</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 1 组：used to vs be used to vs get used to</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">used to /ˈjuːst tuː/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>过去常常（现在不了）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I used to live in Shanghai.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我过去住在上海（现在不住了）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">be used to /biː ˈjuːst tuː/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>习惯于（状态）+ doing</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She is used to getting up early.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她习惯早起了（已经习惯的状态）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get used to /ɡet ˈjuːst tuː/</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>逐渐习惯（过程）+ doing</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? It took me a month to get used to driving on the left.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我花了一个月才习惯靠左行驶（从不会到会的过程）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>used to 后接动词原形，表示过去习惯；be/get used to 后接 doing，表示习惯的状态或过程。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ 易错点：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">❌ I used to watch a movie yesterday（错！yesterday 是单次过去时间，用一般过去时）<br>✅ I watched a movie yesterday</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 2 组：should have vs shouldn\'t have</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">should have + 过去分词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>本应该做却没做（后悔/责备）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? You should have checked the weather forecast.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你本应该查天气预报的（暗示结果淋雨了）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">shouldn\'t have + 过去分词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>本不该做却做了（批评）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She shouldn\'t have said that in front of her boss.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她本不该在老板面前说那话（但她说了）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>should have = 事后诸葛亮，表达\"早知道就...\"</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ 易错点：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">❌ I should have went to bed early（错！went 是过去式，应该用过去分词 gone）<br>✅ I should have gone to bed early</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 3 组：needn\'t have vs didn\'t need to</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">needn\'t have + 过去分词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>本不必做却做了（已做，但多余）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? You needn\'t have bought so many snacks — we ordered pizza!</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你本不必买这么多零食的（但买了），我们点了披萨！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">didn\'t need to + 动词原形</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>不必做（没说做没做）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I didn\'t need to go to work yesterday.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我昨天不必去上班（可能去了，也可能没去）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 核心区别：</strong>needn\'t have done = 做了但多余；didn\'t need to do = 不必做（动作未明确）。</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ 易错点：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">❌ You needn\'t to wait（错！needn\'t 后直接加动词原形，或用 needn\'t have done）<br>✅ You needn\'t wait（现在不必等）<br>✅ You needn\'t have waited（当时不必等，但等了）</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">真题实战：FCE Writing Part 1 邮件</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;border-left:4px solid #28a745\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#28a745;margin:0 0 12px\">✅ 满分范文片段</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0\">\"Thanks for your help with the project! I <em style=\"color:#4a90e2;\">should have asked you sooner</em> — my notes were incomplete. And don\'t worry about the presentation tomorrow: you <em style=\"color:#4a90e2;\">needn\'t have prepared extra slides</em>, as the teacher said we\'ll only show our main findings. By the way, I <em style=\"color:#4a90e2;\">used to work</em> at that café near school — it\'s still open!\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0\"><strong>评分依据：</strong><br>? Grammar (5/5)：三个结构全部正确，时态逻辑严密<br>? Discourse (4/5)：自然衔接，口语化但得体<br>? Lexical Resource (4/5)：avoid repetition — 高分关键</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 小练习</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选 3 组短语各造一个句子，发到评论区，我会逐一批改！</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几组短语？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','FCE 必考！3 大高频易错短语（错误率 85%）— used to/should have/needn\'t have 用法解析 + 真题评分标准','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpcxPAbyoE_IEp18hLBCDjIEQ6iQ1JHN9nW7ZKYklsopO',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_fce_干货','FCE 短语 语法 备考','','',4,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-11 11:53:45','2026-03-11 12:07:05',1,NULL),(51,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpS8qRKnH7vpZpg8XA_hae8WLeYjprnEhkUkW75a2sW8v','FCE 必考！6 大高频易错短语（错误率 90%）','英语陪跑 go','FCE 写作高频易错短语：used to do / be used to doing / get used to doing / should have done / needn\'t have done，90% 考生都混淆！','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\"I <strong>used to play</strong> piano when I was ten.\" — 你写对了，阅卷老师点头；\"She <strong>should have told</strong> me earlier.\" — 语法精准，B2 级逻辑跃然纸上；\"You <strong>needn\'t have waited</strong> — I arrived on time!\" — 这一句，直接拉开与 A2/B1 考生的差距。</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">但考场真实一幕是：一位 FCE 考生在 Writing Part 1（邮件）中写道：I should have known that before ✅，下一行却写：I needn\'t to wait ❌——瞬间扣掉语法分。</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天这 6 个 FCE 高频易错短语，必须掌握！每组都配有真题例句和评分标准，看完再也不丢分！</p>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复关键词<strong>「FCE 短语」</strong>，获取 50 组 FCE 必备短语完整清单！</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 1 组：used to do（过去常常）</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">used to /ˈjuːst tuː/ + 动词原形</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>过去长期、重复的习惯或状态（现已终止）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I used to live in Shanghai.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我过去住在上海（现在不住了）。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He used to smoke, but he quit in 2020.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他过去抽烟，但 2020 年戒了。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ 易错点：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">❌ I used to watch a movie yesterday（错！yesterday 是单次过去时间）<br>✅ I watched a movie yesterday<br><br>❌ Did you used to play football?（错！疑问句用 use to）<br>✅ Did you use to play football?</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 2 组：be used to doing（习惯于）</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">be used to /biː ˈjuːst tuː/ + 动名词 doing</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>已经习惯的<strong>状态</strong>（to 是介词，后接 doing）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She is used to getting up early.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她习惯早起了（已经习惯的状态）。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? They aren\'t used to eating spicy food.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他们不习惯吃辣。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e74c3c\">? 记忆技巧：</strong>be used to = 已经是习惯，to 后面接名词或 doing。</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 3 组：get used to doing（逐渐习惯）</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get used to /ɡet ˈjuːst tuː/ + 动名词 doing</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>从\"不习惯\"到\"习惯\"的<strong>过程</strong>（to 是介词，后接 doing）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? It took me a month to get used to driving on the left.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我花了一个月才习惯靠左行驶（从不会到会的过程）。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? You\'ll soon get used to the new schedule.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你很快就会适应新时间表的。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ used to 家族核心区别：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">? <strong>used to do</strong> = 过去常常（现在不了）→ 后接动词原形<br>? <strong>be used to doing</strong> = 习惯于（状态）→ 后接 doing<br>? <strong>get used to doing</strong> = 逐渐习惯（过程）→ 后接 doing</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 4 组：should have done（本应该做）</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">should have + 过去分词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>本应该做却没做（表达后悔、责备或合理推测）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? You should have checked the weather forecast.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你本应该查天气预报的（暗示结果淋雨了）。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I should have called her yesterday.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我本应该昨天给她打电话的（但没打）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 5 组：shouldn\'t have done（本不该做）</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">shouldn\'t have + 过去分词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>本不该做却做了（表达批评或后悔）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? She shouldn\'t have said that in front of her boss.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她本不该在老板面前说那话（但她说了）。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I shouldn\'t have eaten so much cake.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我本不该吃那么多蛋糕的（但吃了）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ 易错点：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">❌ I should have went to bed early（错！went 是过去式）<br>✅ I should have gone to bed early（should have + 过去分词）</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第 6 组：needn\'t have done（本不必做）</h2>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">needn\'t have + 过去分词</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>本不必做却做了（已做，但事后证明多余）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? You needn\'t have bought so many snacks — we ordered pizza!</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 你本不必买这么多零食的（但买了），我们点了披萨！</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? He needn\'t have worried; everything went smoothly.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他本不必担心的（但担心了），一切都很顺利。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">对比：didn\'t need to + 动词原形</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>用法：</strong>不必做（没说做没做，动作未明确）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">? I didn\'t need to go to work yesterday.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我昨天不必去上班（可能去了，也可能没去）。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fff8e1;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:18px 0;border-left:4px solid #f39c12\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>⚠️ 核心区别：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">? <strong>needn\'t have done</strong> = 做了但多余<br>? <strong>didn\'t need to do</strong> = 不必做（动作未明确）<br><br>❌ You needn\'t to wait（错！needn\'t 后直接加动词原形）<br>✅ You needn\'t wait（现在不必等）<br>✅ You needn\'t have waited（当时不必等，但等了）</p>\n</section>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">真题实战：FCE Writing Part 1 邮件</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;border-left:4px solid #28a745\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#28a745;margin:0 0 12px\">✅ 满分范文片段</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0\">\"Thanks for your help with the project! I <em style=\"color:#4a90e2;\">should have asked you sooner</em> — my notes were incomplete. And don\'t worry about the presentation tomorrow: you <em style=\"color:#4a90e2;\">needn\'t have prepared extra slides</em>, as the teacher said we\'ll only show our main findings. By the way, I <em style=\"color:#4a90e2;\">used to work</em> at that café near school — it\'s still open!\"</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.9;margin:8px 0\"><strong>评分依据：</strong><br>? Grammar (5/5)：三个结构全部正确，时态逻辑严密<br>? Discourse (4/5)：自然衔接，口语化但得体<br>? Lexical Resource (4/5)：avoid repetition — 高分关键</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 小练习</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">选 3 组短语各造一个句子，发到评论区，我会逐一批改！</p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几组短语？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','FCE 必考！6 大高频易错短语（错误率 90%）— used to/be used to/get used to/should have/needn\'t have 用法解析 + 真题评分标准','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpT9it6VC1PCAYa8MGtE6rcCK4AnDGzmBaaEZb1xF24lR',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_fce_干货','FCE 短语 语法 备考','','',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-11 12:08:30','2026-03-11 12:08:43',1,NULL),(52,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpbFwFy0hCc46puJqw4j3UXFnT9z1GwkxEPsdLwjq_jrp','KET 必考！4 个超实用的 turn 短语','Cathy','✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载? 粉丝福利关注公众号，回复「PET 短语」获取本文 PDF 版 + 100 个 PET 高频短语完整清单turn 是 KET/PET 考试中的超高频动词，它和不同副词/介词搭配，意思完全不同！今天这 4 个短语必','<p style=\"color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p><div style=\"background: #4a90e2; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;\"><p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 0;\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「PET 短语」</strong>获取本文 PDF 版 + 100 个 PET 高频短语完整清单</p></div><p style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 15px 0;\">turn 是 KET/PET 考试中的<strong>超高频动词</strong>，它和不同副词/介词搭配，意思完全不同！今天这 4 个短语必须掌握，阅读听力都会考，作文里用上还能加分！</p><hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 25px 0;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">1. turn up - 出现；调大（音量）</h2><div style=\"background: #e8f4fd; border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong style=\"color: #4a90e2;\">turn up</strong> <span style=\"color: #666;\">① 出现，露面 ② 调大（音量等）</span></p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 1（出现）：</strong> He did not turn up at the meeting.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 他没有出席会议。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 2（出现）：</strong> Do not worry, she will turn up soon.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 别担心，她很快就会出现的。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 3（调大）：</strong> Can you turn up the music? I love this song!</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 你能把音乐调大点吗？我喜欢这首歌！</p></div><p style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 15px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">? 记忆技巧：</strong> up 有向上的意思，音量往上调就是调大；人冒出来就是出现。</p><hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 25px 0;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2. turn into sth - 变成，转变为</h2><div style=\"background: #e8f4fd; border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong style=\"color: #4a90e2;\">turn into sth</strong> <span style=\"color: #666;\">变成某物，转变为</span></p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> The caterpillar turned into a butterfly.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 毛毛虫变成了蝴蝶。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> Water turns into ice at 0°C.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 水在 0 摄氏度时变成冰。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> The dream turned into a nightmare.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 美梦变成了噩梦。</p></div><p style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 15px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">? 记忆技巧：</strong> into 表示进入...状态，从一种状态进入另一种状态 = 转变。</p><hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 25px 0;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">3. turn out to be - 结果是，原来是</h2><div style=\"background: #e8f4fd; border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong style=\"color: #4a90e2;\">turn out to be</strong> <span style=\"color: #666;\">结果是，原来是（常指出乎意料）</span></p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> It turned out to be a great day!</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 结果那天过得非常棒！</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> The movie turned out to be boring.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 结果那部电影很无聊。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> He turned out to be my old classmate.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 原来他是我的老同学。</p></div><p style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 15px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">? 记忆技巧：</strong> out 有出来、揭晓的意思，真相出来了 = 结果是。</p><hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 25px 0;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">4. turn sb down - 拒绝某人</h2><div style=\"background: #e8f4fd; border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong style=\"color: #4a90e2;\">turn sb down</strong> <span style=\"color: #666;\">拒绝某人（请求、邀请等）</span></p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> She turned him down when he asked her to dance.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 他邀请她跳舞时，她拒绝了。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> I had to turn down their invitation.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 我不得不拒绝他们的邀请。</p></div><div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> My boss turned down my request for a raise.</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 老板拒绝了我加薪的请求。</p></div><p style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 15px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">? 记忆技巧：</strong> down 有向下的意思，把别人的请求压下去 = 拒绝。</p><hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 25px 0;\"><div style=\"background: #fffbe6; border-left: 4px solid #f39c12; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>? 小练习：</strong> 选 2 个短语各造一个句子，发到评论区，我会逐一批改！</p></div><div style=\"background: #fffbe6; border-left: 4px solid #f39c12; padding: 12px 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50;\"><strong>⚠️ 易错提醒：</strong> turn up/down 可以接音量，也可以接人/请求；turn out to be 后面接结果/身份。</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 2px dashed #ddd;\"><p style=\"color: #2c3e50; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;\">THE END</p><p style=\"color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 10px 0;\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p><p style=\"color: #999; font-size: 13px; margin: 10px 0;\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p><p style=\"color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin: 15px 0 5px;\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p><p style=\"color: #4a90e2; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0;\">回复关键词「PET 短语」获取完整清单</p></div>','','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpevp6fyKkvmJZ1zHPKGEJ17Wp2dTnQRid1j8KDbGY6Sv',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','PET 短语','KET 必考！4 个 turn 短语，阅读听力都考！','KET/PET 必考的 4 个 turn 短语！\n\n1️⃣ turn up - 出现；调大\n2️⃣ turn into - 变成\n3️⃣ turn out to be - 结果是\n4️⃣ turn down - 拒绝\n\n每个都有 2-3 个例句 + 记忆技巧，看完再也不丢分！\n\n#KET #PET #英语短语 #英语学习 #备考技巧',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-12 09:32:27','2026-03-12 09:32:40',1,NULL),(53,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpck85cI8Gt7Is8CsAX1wt03QL7bj_-4oiBpYtLdJvkkq','KET 必考！4 个超实用的 turn 短语','Cathy','✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载turn 是 KET/PET 考试中的超高频动词，它和不同副词/介词搭配，意思完全不同！今天这 4 个短语必须掌握，阅读听力都会考，作文里用上还能加分！? 粉丝福利关注公众号，回复「PET 短语」获取本文 PDF','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">turn 是 KET/PET 考试中的<strong>超高频动词</strong>，它和不同副词/介词搭配，意思完全不同！今天这 4 个短语必须掌握，阅读听力都会考，作文里用上还能加分！</p></section><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「PET 短语」</strong>获取本文 PDF 版 + 100 个 PET 高频短语完整清单</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">1. turn up - 出现；调大（音量）</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn up</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>① 出现，露面 ② 调大（音量等）</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1（出现）：</strong> He did not turn up at the meeting.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 他没有出席会议。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2（出现）：</strong> Do not worry, she will turn up soon.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 别担心，她很快就会出现的。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3（调大）：</strong> Can you turn up the music? I love this song!</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 你能把音乐调大点吗？我喜欢这首歌！</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">up 有向上的意思，音量往上调就是调大；人冒出来就是出现。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2. turn into sth - 变成，转变为</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn into sth</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>变成某物，转变为</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> The caterpillar turned into a butterfly.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 毛毛虫变成了蝴蝶。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> Water turns into ice at 0°C.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 水在 0 摄氏度时变成冰。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> The dream turned into a nightmare.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 美梦变成了噩梦。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">into 表示进入...状态，从一种状态进入另一种状态 = 转变。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">3. turn out to be - 结果是，原来是</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn out to be</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>结果是，原来是（常指出乎意料）</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> It turned out to be a great day!</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 结果那天过得非常棒！</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> The movie turned out to be boring.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 结果那部电影很无聊。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> He turned out to be my old classmate.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 原来他是我的老同学。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">out 有出来、揭晓的意思，真相出来了 = 结果是。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">4. turn sb down - 拒绝某人</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn sb down</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>拒绝某人（请求、邀请等）</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> She turned him down when he asked her to dance.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 他邀请她跳舞时，她拒绝了。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> I had to turn down their invitation.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 我不得不拒绝他们的邀请。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> My boss turned down my request for a raise.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 老板拒绝了我加薪的请求。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">down 有向下的意思，把别人的请求压下去 = 拒绝。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;padding:12px 15px;margin:20px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>? 小练习：</strong> 选 2 个短语各造一个句子，发到评论区，我会逐一批改！</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;padding:12px 15px;margin:20px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>⚠️ 易错提醒：</strong> turn up/down 可以接音量，也可以接人/请求；turn out to be 后面接结果/身份。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几个短语？</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p><p style=\"color:#4a90e2;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin:15px 0\">回复关键词「PET 短语」获取完整清单</p></section>','','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpS-xPL6M79SGG51FGoFx2mcLSwB78T2R-8mGBKAOgHzN',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','PET 短语','KET 必考！4 个 turn 短语，阅读听力都考！','KET/PET 必考的 4 个 turn 短语！\n\n1️⃣ turn up - 出现；调大\n2️⃣ turn into - 变成\n3️⃣ turn out to be - 结果是\n4️⃣ turn down - 拒绝\n\n每个都有 2-3 个例句 + 记忆技巧，看完再也不丢分！\n\n#KET #PET #英语短语 #英语学习 #备考技巧',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-12 10:47:49','2026-03-12 10:48:10',1,NULL),(54,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpcD9L8vCRe0OpbcN-715CEAQtQoB2Wi2q142yNjSvrjb','4 个超实用的跟 turn 相关的短语','Cathy','✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载? 粉丝福利关注公众号，回复「PET 短语」获取本文 PDF 版 + 100 个 PET 高频短语完整清单turn 是 KET/PET 包括中考考试中的超高频动词，它和不同副词/介词搭配，意思完全不同！今天这 4','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「PET 短语」</strong>获取本文 PDF 版 + 100 个 PET 高频短语完整清单</p></section><section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">turn 是 KET/PET 包括中考考试中的<strong>超高频动词</strong>，它和不同副词/介词搭配，意思完全不同！今天这 4 个短语必须掌握，阅读听力都会考，作文里用上还能加分！</p></section><section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">turn on 打开...<br>turn off 关闭...<br>咱们就跳过啦～</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">1. turn up - 出现、露面 / 调大音量</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn up</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>① 出现，露面 ② 调大（音量等）</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1（出现，露面）：</strong> He did not turn up at the meeting.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 他没有出席会议。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2（出现）：</strong> Do not worry, she will turn up soon.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 别担心，她很快就会出现的。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3（调大）：</strong> Can you turn up the music? I love this song!</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 你能把音乐调大点吗？我喜欢这首歌！</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">up 有向上的意思，音量往上调就是调大；人冒出来就是出现。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2. turn into sth - 变成，转变为</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn into sth</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>变成某物，转变为</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> The caterpillar turned into a butterfly.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 毛毛虫变成了蝴蝶。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> Water turns into ice at 0°C.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 水在 0 摄氏度时变成冰。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> The dream turned into a nightmare.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 美梦变成了噩梦。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">into 表示进入...状态，从一种状态进入另一种状态 = 转变。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">3. turn out to be - 结果是，原来是</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn out to be</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>结果是，原来是（常指出乎意料）</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> It turned out to be a great day!</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 结果那天过得非常棒！</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> The movie turned out to be boring.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 结果那部电影很无聊。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> He turned out to be my old classmate.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 原来他是我的老同学。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">out 有出来、揭晓的意思，真相出来了 = 结果是。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">4. turn sb down - 拒绝某人</h2></section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">turn sb down</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>释义：</strong>拒绝某人（请求、邀请等）</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 1：</strong> She turned him down when he asked her to dance.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 他邀请她跳舞时，她拒绝了。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 2：</strong> I had to turn down their invitation.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 我不得不拒绝他们的邀请。</p></section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>例句 3：</strong> My boss turned down my request for a raise.</p><p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\"><strong>翻译：</strong> 老板拒绝了我加薪的请求。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">down 有向下的意思，把别人的请求压下去 = 拒绝。</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;padding:12px 15px;margin:20px 0;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>? 复习时间：</strong></p><p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:2\">turn up 1️⃣出现 2️⃣调高音量<br>turn into 变成<br>turn out to be 原来是，结果是<br>turn sth/sb down 拒绝....</p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\"><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">THE END</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p><p style=\"color:#4a90e2;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin:15px 0\">回复关键词「PET 短语」获取完整清单</p></section>','','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpdeRkHzfbofhFaRa2s6JwK1Jxf9uf4khfA1SlLy5C2vR',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','PET 短语','4 个超实用的 turn 短语，阅读听力都考！','4 个超实用的 turn 短语！\n\n1️⃣ turn up - 出现；调大\n2️⃣ turn into - 变成\n3️⃣ turn out to be - 结果是\n4️⃣ turn down - 拒绝\n\n每个都有 2-3 个例句 + 记忆技巧，看完再也不丢分！\n\n#KET #PET #英语短语 #英语学习 #备考技巧',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-12 12:56:57','2026-03-12 12:57:25',1,NULL),(55,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpeXmS8dv0qaivM5guQ25ISs8MC-96bXUya1bab31U65c','英语里这 5 个谐音梗，老外笑了你还没懂','Cathy','英语里有一种冷笑话，叫 Pun（谐音梗/双关语）。老外讲起来笑到停不下来，你听完一脸懵——这也能笑？今天给你 5 个超经典的英语谐音梗，看完你也能 get 到老外的笑点，还能自己造！1. Why is 6 afraid of 7? Beca','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px;\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</span></p></section><section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff;\"><p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 粉丝福利</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">关注公众号，回复</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">「英语谐音」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">获取 50 个英语谐音梗完整 PDF + 使用场景指南</span></p></section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">英语里有一种\"冷笑话\"，叫</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Pun（谐音梗/双关语）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">老外讲起来笑到停不下来，你听完一脸懵——</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">\"这也能笑？\"</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">今天给你</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">5 个超经典的英语谐音梗</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，看完你也能 get 到老外的笑点，还能自己造！</span></p><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:#2f76c3;\">1. Why is 6 afraid of 7?</span></h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谐音梗解析</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">问：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">为什么 6 怕 7？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">答：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Because 7</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> ate </span></strong><span leaf=\"\">9!</span></p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 笑点在哪？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">ate（吃）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">和</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> eight（8）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">发音完全一样！</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;表面看是\"7 吃了 9\"，听起来像\"789\"——数字排队，6 当然怕被吃掉啦！</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这是英语里最经典的谐音梗之一，小朋友都在讲～</span></p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:#2f76c3;\">2. What do you call a fake noodle?</span></h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谐音梗解析</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">问：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">假面条叫什么？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">答：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">An</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> impasta</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">!</span></p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 笑点在哪？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">impasta</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">=</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> imposter（骗子）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">+</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> pasta（意大利面）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">！</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;假面条 = 骗人的面 = impasta，完美双关！</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这类造词梗在英语里超常见，老外爱死了～</span></p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:#2f76c3;\">3. Why dont eggs tell jokes?</span></h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谐音梗解析</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">问：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">鸡蛋为什么不讲笑话？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">答：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Because theyd</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> crack each other up</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">!</span></p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 笑点在哪？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">crack up</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">有两个意思：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;①</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">（鸡蛋）裂开</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;②</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">笑到停不下来</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;鸡蛋讲笑话会互相\"crack up\"——既指笑到崩，也指物理裂开，双关满分！</span></p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:#2f76c3;\">4. What do you call a bear with no teeth?</span></h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谐音梗解析</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">问：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">没牙的熊叫什么？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">答：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">A</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> gummy bear</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">!</span></p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 笑点在哪？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">gummy</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">有两个意思：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;①</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">牙龈的、没牙的</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（gum=牙龈）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;②</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">软糖</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（gummy bear= 小熊软糖）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;没牙的熊 = 牙龈熊 = 小熊软糖，可爱又机智！</span></p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:#2f76c3;\">5. Why did the bicycle fall over?</span></h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2;\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谐音梗解析</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">问：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">自行车为什么倒了？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">答：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Because it was</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> two-tired</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">!</span></p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 笑点在哪？</span></p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">two-tired</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">=</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"> too tired（太累了）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">！</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;同时自行车确实有</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">两个轮胎（two tires）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，双重含义完美契合！</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这类\"数字 + 单词\"谐音在英语里超常见～</span></p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623;\"><p style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;text-align:center;margin:0 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 一句话总结</span></p><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:15px 0;\"><tbody><tr style=\"background:#fff;\"><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">谐音梗类型</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;color:#3a3a3a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">例子</span></section></td></tr><tr style=\"background:#fff;\"><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">同音异义</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;color:#3a3a3a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">ate / eight</span></section></td></tr><tr style=\"background:#fff;\"><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">造词双关</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;color:#3a3a3a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">impasta = imposter + pasta</span></section></td></tr><tr style=\"background:#fff;\"><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">一词多义</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;color:#3a3a3a;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">crack up / gummy / two-tired</span></section></td></tr></tbody></table></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;padding:12px 15px;margin:20px 0;border-radius:4px;\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">? 复习时间：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">ate = eight（8）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">impasta = imposter + pasta</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">crack up = 裂开 / 笑崩</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">gummy = 牙龈的 / 软糖</span><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span><span leaf=\"\">two-tired = too tired / 两个轮胎</span></p></section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0;\"  /><section style=\"margin:30px 0;padding:25px;background:#28a745;border-radius:12px;color:#fff;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(40,167,69,0.3);\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 15px;font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 结尾金句</span></p><p style=\"margin:0 0 15px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-style:italic;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"英语谐音梗不是冷笑话，是语言的双人舞——听懂了，你就入了门。\"</span></p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;opacity:0.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">下次老外讲 pun，别愣着，跟着笑就对了！</span></p></section><section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0;\"><p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:20px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 觉得有用，记得点赞 + 收藏，下次讲给老外听！</span></p><p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:15px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 留言区打卡：你最想讲给谁听？</span></p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">— THE END —</span></p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</span></p><p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</span></p><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</span></p><p style=\"color:#4a90e2;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin:15px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">回复关键词「英语谐音」获取完整 PDF</span></p></section><p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>','英语里有一种冷笑话，叫 Pun（谐音梗/双关语）。老外讲起来笑到停不下来，你听完一脸懵——这也能笑？今天给你 5 个超经典的英语谐音梗，看完你也能 get 到老外的笑点，还能自己造！1. Why is 6 afraid of 7? Because 7 ate 9! 2. What do you call a fake noodle? An impasta! 3. Why dont eggs tell jokes? Because theyd crack each other up! 4. What do you call a bear with no teeth? A gummy bear! 5. Why did the bicycle fall over? Because it was two-tired!','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpS3c5ZWgVEDyJv7Yvuu2ZIvK-fV44Mctybv299oCfTYd',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','英语谐音梗','英语谐音梗?老外笑了你还没懂？这 5 个 pun 绝了','英语谐音梗大合集！?\n\n1️⃣ Why is 6 afraid of 7?\nBecause 7 ate 9!\n（ate=eight，8 吃了 9?）\n\n2️⃣ What do you call a fake noodle?\nAn impasta!\n（imposter+pasta，假面条=骗子面）\n\n3️⃣ Why dont eggs tell jokes?\nBecause theyd crack each other up!\n（crack up=裂开/笑崩）\n\n4️⃣ What do you call a bear with no teeth?\nA gummy bear!\n（gummy=牙龈的/软糖）\n\n5️⃣ Why did the bicycle fall over?\nBecause it was two-tired!\n（two-tired=too tired/两个轮胎）\n\n? 谐音梗不是冷笑话，是语言的双人舞～\n\n#英语谐音梗 #英语学习 #英语冷笑话 #pun #英语陪跑 go',2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-15 14:07:07','2026-03-15 14:07:15',1,NULL),(56,NULL,'英语写作必备｜4 个递进关系词，让你的文章逻辑更清晰','Cathy','写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 and 连接句子？想要表达而且、此外、更重要的是，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 \"and\" 连接句子？想要表达\"而且\"、\"此外\"、\"更重要的是\"，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 四个递进关系词详解</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作模板资料！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. Besides</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>口语化，较轻松</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>除了...之外（还有），况且</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">Besides English, she speaks French and Spanish.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 除了英语，她还会说法语和西班牙语。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:8px 0 0\">I don\'t want to go. Besides, I\'m too tired.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我不想去。况且，我也太累了。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. What\'s more</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>中等正式，略带强调</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>更重要的是，而且</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">He finished on time. What\'s more, he exceeded expectations.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他按时完成了。更重要的是，他超出了预期。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:8px 0 0\">The apartment is bright. What\'s more, the rent is reasonable.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 公寓很明亮。而且，租金很合理。</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. In addition</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>正式，中性</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>此外，另外</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">In addition to his duties, he manages the team.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 除了日常工作外，他还负责管理团队。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:8px 0 0\">The company offers insurance. In addition, employees get paid vacation.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 公司提供保险。此外，员工还有带薪休假。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Furthermore</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>非常正式</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>此外，而且（进一步说明）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The evidence is inconclusive. Furthermore, the methodology has flaws.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 证据并不确凿。此外，研究方法也有缺陷。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:8px 0 0\">Smoking is harmful. Furthermore, it affects people around you.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 吸烟有害健康。而且，它还会影响周围的人。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 使用建议</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    <strong>日常聊天/社交媒体</strong> → Besides 或 What\'s more<br>\n    <strong>工作邮件/商务文档</strong> → In addition<br>\n    <strong>学术论文/正式报告</strong> → Furthermore 或 In addition<br>\n    <strong>想要强调\"更重要的是\"</strong> → What\'s more\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几个递进词？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语连接词进阶篇</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 and 连接句子？想要表达而且、此外、更重要的是，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！Besides 口语化较轻松除了之外况且 What\'s more 中等正式略带强调更重要的是而且 In addition 正式中性此外另外 Furthermore 非常正式此外而且进一步说明 使用建议：日常聊天社交媒体用 Besides 或 What\'s more，工作邮件商务文档用 In addition，学术论文正式报告用 Furthermore 或 In addition。','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpY0f2eO-LKexdkn0v7TwQxLnGgU4GHJUQNPH-CquGifz',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','写作技巧','英语写作必备｜4 个递进关系词，逻辑更清晰','写英语文章只会用 and？\n\n今天讲透 4 个高频递进词：\n\n1. Besides - 口语化，况且\n2. What\'s more - 强调更重要的是\n3. In addition - 正式中性，此外\n4. Furthermore - 最正式，论文必备\n\n每个词都配了例句，一看就懂！\n\n使用场景：\n日常聊天 → Besides/What\'s more\n工作邮件 → In addition\n学术论文 → Furthermore\n\n收藏备用，写作不卡壳！\n\n#英语写作 #连接词 #英语学习 #英语语法 #写作技巧',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-18 09:27:40','2026-03-18 09:30:57',1,NULL),(57,NULL,'英语写作必备｜4 个递进关系词，让你的文章逻辑更清晰','Cathy','写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 and 连接句子？想要表达而且、此外、更重要的是，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！每个词都配有详细用法说明、多个例句和记忆技巧，建议收藏慢慢看～','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 \"and\" 连接句子？想要表达\"而且\"、\"此外\"、\"更重要的是\"，却总想不出合适的词？</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 <strong>4 个高频递进关系词</strong>，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！每个词都配有详细用法说明、多个例句和记忆技巧，建议收藏慢慢看～</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 四个递进关系词详解</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作模板资料！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. Besides</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>口语化，较轻松</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>除了...之外（还有），况且</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首（最常见）、句中</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">Besides English, she speaks French and Spanish.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 除了英语，她还会说法语和西班牙语。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">I don\'t want to go to the party. Besides, I\'m too tired.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我不想去派对。况且，我也太累了。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The hotel was cheap. Besides, it was close to the beach.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这家酒店很便宜。而且，它离海滩很近。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">Besides = \"比\"（besides 开头）+ \" sides\"（边）→ \"在旁边还有\" → \"除此之外\"</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. What\'s more</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>中等正式，略带强调</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>更重要的是，而且</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首（几乎总是）</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">He got the job done on time. What\'s more, he exceeded all expectations.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他按时完成了工作。更重要的是，他超出了所有预期。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The apartment is spacious and bright. What\'s more, the rent is very reasonable.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这套公寓宽敞明亮。而且，租金非常合理。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">She\'s an excellent teacher. What\'s more, she truly cares about her students.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她是一位优秀的老师。更重要的是，她真心关心她的学生。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 使用场景</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">当你想强调后面补充的信息<strong>更重要</strong>或<strong>更有说服力</strong>时，用 What\'s more！带有\"不仅如此，还有更厉害的\"的语气。</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. In addition</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>正式，中性</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>此外，另外</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首、句中</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">In addition to his regular duties, he manages the team.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 除了日常工作外，他还负责管理团队。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The company offers health insurance. In addition, employees receive paid vacation.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 公司提供健康保险。此外，员工还享有带薪休假。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">We need to reduce costs. In addition, we should improve efficiency.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们需要降低成本。另外，我们还应该提高效率。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 使用场景</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">最<strong>中性、最安全</strong>的递进词！适合学术写作、商务邮件、正式文档。单纯表示\"另外还有一件事\"，不带强调色彩。</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Furthermore</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>非常正式</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>此外，而且（进一步说明）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首（最常见）</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The evidence is inconclusive. Furthermore, the methodology has serious flaws.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 证据并不确凿。此外，研究方法也存在严重缺陷。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The project is over budget. Furthermore, it\'s behind schedule.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这个项目超预算了。而且，进度也落后了。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">Smoking is harmful to your health. Furthermore, it affects people around you.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 吸烟有害健康。而且，它还会影响你周围的人。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 使用场景</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">四个词中<strong>最正式</strong>的一个！常用于学术论文、正式报告、法律文件。表示在前文基础上<strong>进一步深入</strong>论证。</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 对比总结表</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    <strong>Besides</strong> → ⭐⭐ 较随意，口语化，\"况且\"<br>\n    <strong>What\'s more</strong> → ⭐⭐⭐ 中等，强调\"更重要的是\"<br>\n    <strong>In addition</strong> → ⭐⭐⭐⭐ 正式，中性，\"此外\"<br>\n    <strong>Furthermore</strong> → ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 非常正式，深入论证\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 使用建议</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    <strong>日常聊天/社交媒体</strong> → Besides 或 What\'s more<br>\n    <strong>工作邮件/商务文档</strong> → In addition<br>\n    <strong>学术论文/正式报告</strong> → Furthermore 或 In addition<br>\n    <strong>想要强调\"更重要的是\"</strong> → What\'s more\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几个递进词？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语连接词进阶篇</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n','写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 and 连接句子？想要表达而且、此外、更重要的是，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！每个词都配有详细用法说明、多个例句和记忆技巧。Besides 口语化较轻松除了之外况且 What\'s more 中等正式略带强调更重要的是而且 In addition 正式中性此外另外 Furthermore 非常正式此外而且进一步说明 使用建议：日常聊天社交媒体用 Besides 或 What\'s more，工作邮件商务文档用 In addition，学术论文正式报告用 Furthermore 或 In addition。','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpaihSEWvWTXDzPrl7fSO9mXzKr5O3PsXfdO0RFBquDKJ',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','写作技巧','英语写作必备｜4 个递进关系词，逻辑更清晰','写英语文章只会用 and？\n\n今天讲透 4 个高频递进词：\n\n1. Besides - 口语化，况且\n2. What\'s more - 强调更重要的是\n3. In addition - 正式中性，此外\n4. Furthermore - 最正式，论文必备\n\n每个词都配了 3 个例句 + 记忆技巧，一看就懂！\n\n使用场景：\n日常聊天 → Besides/What\'s more\n工作邮件 → In addition\n学术论文 → Furthermore\n\n收藏备用，写作不卡壳！\n\n#英语写作 #连接词 #英语学习 #英语语法 #写作技巧',5,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-18 09:31:32','2026-03-18 09:40:25',1,NULL),(58,NULL,'英语写作必备｜4 个递进关系词，让你的文章逻辑更清晰','Cathy','写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 and 连接句子？想要表达而且、此外、更重要的是，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 \"and\" 连接句子？想要表达\"而且\"、\"此外\"、\"更重要的是\"，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！每个词都配有详细用法说明、多个例句和记忆技巧，建议收藏慢慢看～</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 四个递进关系词详解</h2>\n\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>，获取写作模板资料！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">1. Besides</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>口语化，较轻松</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>除了...之外（还有），况且</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首（最常见）、句中</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">Besides English, she speaks French and Spanish.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 除了英语，她还会说法语和西班牙语。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">I don\'t want to go to the party. Besides, I\'m too tired.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我不想去派对。况且，我也太累了。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The hotel was cheap. Besides, it was close to the beach.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这家酒店很便宜。而且，它离海滩很近。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">Besides = \"比\"（besides 开头）+ \" sides\"（边）→ \"在旁边还有\" → \"除此之外\"</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">2. What\'s more</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>中等正式，略带强调</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>更重要的是，而且</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首（几乎总是）</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">He got the job done on time. What\'s more, he exceeded all expectations.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 他按时完成了工作。更重要的是，他超出了所有预期。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The apartment is spacious and bright. What\'s more, the rent is very reasonable.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这套公寓宽敞明亮。而且，租金非常合理。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">She\'s an excellent teacher. What\'s more, she truly cares about her students.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 她是一位优秀的老师。更重要的是，她真心关心她的学生。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 使用场景</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">当你想强调后面补充的信息<strong>更重要</strong>或<strong>更有说服力</strong>时，用 What\'s more！带有\"不仅如此，还有更厉害的\"的语气。</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"margin:32px 0\"></p>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">3. In addition</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>正式，中性</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>此外，另外</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首、句中</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">In addition to his regular duties, he manages the team.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 除了日常工作外，他还负责管理团队。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The company offers health insurance. In addition, employees receive paid vacation.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 公司提供健康保险。此外，员工还享有带薪休假。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">We need to reduce costs. In addition, we should improve efficiency.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 我们需要降低成本。另外，我们还应该提高效率。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 使用场景</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">最<strong>中性、最安全</strong>的递进词！适合学术写作、商务邮件、正式文档。单纯表示\"另外还有一件事\"，不带强调色彩。</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">4. Furthermore</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>语气：</strong>非常正式</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>含义：</strong>此外，而且（进一步说明）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:8px 0 6px\"><strong>位置：</strong>句首（最常见）</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 1</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The evidence is inconclusive. Furthermore, the methodology has serious flaws.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 证据并不确凿。此外，研究方法也存在严重缺陷。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">The project is over budget. Furthermore, it\'s behind schedule.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 这个项目超预算了。而且，进度也落后了。</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:12px 0 6px\">? 例句 3</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;font-style:italic;margin:0\">Smoking is harmful to your health. Furthermore, it affects people around you.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:4px 0 0\">— 吸烟有害健康。而且，它还会影响你周围的人。</p>\n  \n  <section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:12px 14px;margin:14px 0 0\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 使用场景</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">四个词中<strong>最正式</strong>的一个！常用于学术论文、正式报告、法律文件。表示在前文基础上<strong>进一步深入</strong>论证。</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 对比总结表</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    <strong>Besides</strong> → ⭐⭐ 较随意，口语化，\"况且\"<br>\n    <strong>What\'s more</strong> → ⭐⭐⭐ 中等，强调\"更重要的是\"<br>\n    <strong>In addition</strong> → ⭐⭐⭐⭐ 正式，中性，\"此外\"<br>\n    <strong>Furthermore</strong> → ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 非常正式，深入论证\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 使用建议</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n    <strong>日常聊天/社交媒体</strong> → Besides 或 What\'s more<br>\n    <strong>工作邮件/商务文档</strong> → In addition<br>\n    <strong>学术论文/正式报告</strong> → Furthermore 或 In addition<br>\n    <strong>想要强调\"更重要的是\"</strong> → What\'s more\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得分享给需要的人！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡：今天学会了哪几个递进词？</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 下期：英语连接词进阶篇</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:11px;margin:4px 0\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>','写英语文章时，是不是经常只会用 and 连接句子？想要表达而且、此外、更重要的是，却总想不出合适的词？今天这篇文章，一次性讲透 4 个高频递进关系词，让你的英语写作逻辑更清晰、表达更地道！','-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpXZQ_tGeC0ZbuJEzEXmeC4OwLxB8MUQwb3aRy3uciUf7',NULL,1,0,0,'ai_auto','写作技巧',NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-18 09:40:25','2026-03-18 09:40:25',1,NULL),(59,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpVLiFIV9Wj6rnuo4uCpdbWwfalA3LbIAZu4fLgilspnI','这5句中式英语，说出口外教当场沉默——你肯定也说过','英语陪跑go','99%的中国人都说错过的5句话，错误原因逐句拆解，看完再也不会说错！','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「中式英语」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n你有没有这种经历：明明觉得自己说的是英语，外教却一脸困惑地看着你……<br><br>\n别怪外教，这5句话，<strong>99%的中国人都说错过</strong>，而且错得非常有规律——全是把中文直接翻译过去。<br><br>\n今天逐句拆解，看完再也不会说错！\n</p>\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">❌ 第1句：I very like English.</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#fdecea;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#c0392b;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❌ 错误：</strong>I very like English.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0\"><strong>✅ 正确：</strong>I like English very much. / I really like English.</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  <strong>为什么错？</strong>very 是副词，不能直接修饰动词。<br>\n  修饰动词要用 very much（放句末）或 really（放动词前）。<br><br>\n  记住：<strong>very + 形容词/副词，不能 + 动词</strong>\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">❌ 第2句：How to say this word?</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#fdecea;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#c0392b;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❌ 错误：</strong>How to say this word?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0\"><strong>✅ 正确：</strong>How do you say this word? / What does this word mean?</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  \"How to...\" 是<strong>从句/短语</strong>，不是完整的疑问句。<br>\n  问别人\"这词怎么说\"要说 How do you say...，加主语和助动词才完整。\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">❌ 第3句：I am 18 years old age.</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#fdecea;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#c0392b;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❌ 错误：</strong>I am 18 years old age.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0\"><strong>✅ 正确：</strong>I am 18 years old. / I am 18.</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  years old 已经包含了年龄的意思，不需要再加 age。<br>\n  这是典型的<strong>中文思维直译</strong>——\"18岁\"→\"18 years old age\"，多了一个 age。\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">❌ 第4句：Yesterday I have been to the mall.</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#fdecea;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#c0392b;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❌ 错误：</strong>Yesterday I have been to the mall.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0\"><strong>✅ 正确：</strong>I went to the mall yesterday.</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  有 yesterday 这类明确过去时间词，<strong>必须用一般过去时</strong>，不能用现在完成时。<br>\n  现在完成时（have been）不和 yesterday / last week / ago 连用，这是KET/PET必考考点！\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">❌ 第5句：He is a very success man.</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#fdecea;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #e74c3c\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#c0392b;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❌ 错误：</strong>He is a very success man.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#27ae60;margin:0\"><strong>✅ 正确：</strong>He is a very successful man.</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">\n  success 是<strong>名词</strong>，修饰名词要用<strong>形容词</strong> successful。<br>\n  中文\"成功的人\"直接用\"成功\"，英文必须变形：success → successful。\n  </p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;text-align:center;margin:0 0 12px\">? 5句总结</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n    ❌ I very like → ✅ I really like / like very much<br>\n    ❌ How to say → ✅ How do you say<br>\n    ❌ years old age → ✅ years old<br>\n    ❌ have been + yesterday → ✅ went<br>\n    ❌ success man → ✅ successful man\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得点赞 + 收藏！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpQV0KZvI2Npby82KZ-igyZ2zCcZG8pjp1HbS8JOSDjKF',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 12:55:41','2026-03-19 12:55:41',0,NULL),(60,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUafCmhW0MBai5d0gNSIPWWtcFhz9kN7xVoVyBL4sVx1','get 不只是\"得到\"！5种用法 KET/PET 每次必考','英语陪跑go','get是英语里用法最多的动词，KET/PET几乎每次必考。5种核心用法+例句，全部掌握阅读写作同步提升！','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「KET资料」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\nget 是英语里用法最多的动词之一，KET/PET 几乎每次必考。<br><br>\n很多同学只知道 get = 得到，其实它有 <strong>5 种完全不同的核心用法</strong>，每种都有专属场景，用对了句子瞬间高级一档！\n</p>\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">1. get = 得到、获得</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get sth</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\"><strong>释义：</strong>得到，获得</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>I got a new phone for my birthday.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">我生日得到了一部新手机。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>She got the first prize in the competition.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">她在比赛中获得了一等奖。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>Can you get me a glass of water?</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">你能帮我拿杯水吗？</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">get 最基本的用法，记住\"get = 拿到手\"就对了！</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2. get = 变得（get + 形容词）</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get + adj.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\"><strong>释义：</strong>变得、逐渐…（表示状态变化）</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>It\'s getting cold outside. Bring a jacket!</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">外面越来越冷了，带件外套！</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>Don\'t worry, you\'ll get better soon.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">别担心，你很快会好起来的。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>He got angry when he heard the news.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">听到这个消息他生气了。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">get + 形容词 = 变得...。常见搭配：get cold/hot/better/worse/tired/angry。这是KET/PET写作加分句型！</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">3. get to = 到达</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get to + 地点</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\"><strong>释义：</strong>到达某地（比 arrive 更口语）</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>What time do you get to school?</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">你几点到学校？</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>We got to the airport just in time.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">我们刚好赶到机场。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>How do I get to the nearest station?</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">我怎么去最近的车站？</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">区分 get to（到达）和 get（得到）：看后面有没有地点！get to school = 到学校，不是\"得到学校\"。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">4. get up = 起床</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get up</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\"><strong>释义：</strong>起床（KET/PET必考短语）</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>I usually get up at 7 o\'clock.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">我通常7点起床。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>She got up late and missed the bus.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">她起床晚了，错过了公共汽车。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>Get up! You\'ll be late for school.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">起床！你上学要迟到了。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">get up 和 wake up 的区别：wake up = 醒来，get up = 从床上起来。可以先 wake up，然后 get up。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5. get on/along with = 与...相处</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:bold;color:#4a90e2;margin:0 0 6px\">get on/along with sb</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0\"><strong>释义：</strong>与某人相处得好（关系类话题必考）</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>I get on well with my classmates.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">我和同学相处得很好。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>Do you get along with your neighbours?</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">你和邻居相处得好吗？</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #3498db;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>She doesn\'t get on with her sister.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666\">她和她姐姐处不好。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:24px 0\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 记忆技巧</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">get on with = get along with，两个意思相同，都是\"相处\"。后面记得加 well 表示\"相处得好\"。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;padding:12px 15px;margin:20px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50\"><strong>? 5种用法速记：</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:2\">\n    get sth → 得到<br>\n    get + adj. → 变得...<br>\n    get to → 到达<br>\n    get up → 起床<br>\n    get on/along with → 相处\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得点赞 + 收藏！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpQV0KZvI2Npby82KZ-igyZ2zCcZG8pjp1HbS8JOSDjKF',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 12:55:45','2026-03-19 12:55:45',0,NULL),(61,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpeJ5pgIEnkzFrPUg9lOmf_tvUH3zhRm6oSZs7CTzByAK','KET/PET 英语作文开头不知道怎么写？5个万能句型直接套用','英语陪跑go','覆盖KET/PET所有常见话题的5个万能开头句型，记叙文、议论文、邮件全搞定！','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「写作」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">\n\"英语作文第一句不知道怎么写\"——这应该是 <strong>KET/PET 考生最常说的一句话</strong>了。<br><br>\n开头句写好了，后面就顺了。今天给你 <strong>5 个万能开头句型</strong>，覆盖 KET/PET 所有常见话题，直接套用！\n</p>\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #27ae60;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 句型1：引出话题型</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 8px\">句型模板</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>Nowadays, more and more people are + doing...</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666;margin:0\">如今，越来越多的人正在……</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #27ae60;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:15px;color:#2c3e50\">? <em>Nowadays, more and more students are learning English online.</em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:#666\">如今，越来越多的学生在网上学英语。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #27ae60;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:15px;color:#2c3e50\">? <em>Nowadays, more and more families are going on trips during holidays.</em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:#666\">如今，越来越多的家庭在假期外出旅行。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 适用话题</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">科技、环境、教育、旅行、健康——几乎万能！</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #27ae60;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 句型2：个人经历型</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>I will never forget the time when...</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666;margin:0\">我永远不会忘记……那次经历</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #27ae60;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:15px;color:#2c3e50\">? <em>I will never forget the time when I won my first English competition.</em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:#666\">我永远不会忘记第一次赢得英语比赛时的情景。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 适用话题</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">记叙文、难忘的经历、关于朋友/家人、旅游——有画面感，阅卷老师爱看！</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #27ae60;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 句型3：提问引入型</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>Have you ever wondered why...?</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666;margin:0\">你有没有想过为什么……？</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #27ae60;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:15px;color:#2c3e50\">? <em>Have you ever wondered why some people learn languages so easily?</em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:#666\">你有没有想过为什么有些人学语言那么轻松？</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 适用话题</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">议论文开头神句！引发读者思考，高分必备。PET写作用上这句，阅卷官眼睛一亮。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #27ae60;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 句型4：场景描述型</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>It was a + 形容词 + 天气/日期, when...</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666;margin:0\">那是一个……的日子，当时……</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #27ae60;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:15px;color:#2c3e50\">? <em>It was a sunny Saturday morning when my family decided to go camping.</em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:#666\">那是一个阳光明媚的周六早晨，我的家人决定去露营。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 适用话题</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">记叙文神开头，画面感超强。天气词换一换，适合所有故事类作文。</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #27ae60;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">? 句型5：观点表达型</h2>\n<section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2c3e50;margin:0 0 6px\"><strong>In my opinion, ... is one of the most important things in life.</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666;margin:0\">在我看来，……是生活中最重要的事之一。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #27ae60;padding:12px 15px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:15px;color:#2c3e50\">? <em>In my opinion, learning English is one of the most important skills in today\'s world.</em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:#666\">在我看来，在当今世界，学习英语是最重要的技能之一。</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 4px\">? 适用话题</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5d4037;margin:0\">议论文、邮件、写作Part2，直接亮出观点，逻辑清晰，阅卷老师最爱！</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;text-align:center;margin:0 0 12px\">? 5个开头句快速对照</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n    ? 引出话题 → Nowadays, more and more...<br>\n    ? 个人经历 → I will never forget the time when...<br>\n    ❓ 提问引入 → Have you ever wondered why...?<br>\n    ? 场景描述 → It was a sunny day when...<br>\n    ? 观点表达 → In my opinion, ... is one of the most...\n  </p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得点赞 + 收藏！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpQV0KZvI2Npby82KZ-igyZ2zCcZG8pjp1HbS8JOSDjKF',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 12:55:49','2026-03-19 12:55:49',0,NULL),(62,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpUCS4iPkGjGlqSh_un7mS808u6bwK91X0UJTLei30fJO','高考英语要降到100分？家长别慌，我说说真实影响','英语陪跑go','两会提案引发家长群热议：高考英语降分对KET/PET备考有没有影响？听说能力反而更重要了。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「备考指南」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">今年两会，一个提案让家长群炸了锅：<strong>有委员建议把高考英语从150分降到100分。</strong><br><br>消息一出，各种声音都来了——有人说终于松口气，有人说完了英语更没人重视，还有人直接在家长群里问：<strong>\"那KET/PET还要不要考？\"</strong><br><br>作为每天研究英语备考的人，我来说说我的看法，帮你把这件事看清楚。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">01 提案说了什么，先搞清楚</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">提案核心内容：<br><strong>① 高考英语总分从150分→100分</strong><br><strong>② 增加听说比重，减少笔试压力</strong><br><strong>③ 理由是：减轻学生负担，缩小城乡差距</strong><br><br>⚠️ 注意：这只是<strong>提案</strong>，不是已经通过的政策，距离真正落地还有很长的路。</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 历史参考</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">英语高考改革喊了很多年，北京、上海已有一考变多考的改革，但150分的权重在大多数省份基本没变。政策变化比你想的慢很多。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">02 对KET/PET有没有影响？</h2><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">直接说结论：<strong>没有影响，甚至更重要了。</strong></p><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  <strong>高考英语降分</strong> ≠ 英语不重要<br><br>\n  KET/PET是剑桥国际认证，和高考是两套体系：<br>\n  ? 国际学校申请 → 看KET/PET，不看高考<br>\n  ? 出国留学背景 → 国际英语认证更有含金量<br>\n  ? 简历竞争力 → 剑桥证书全球认可<br><br>\n  而且，如果高考英语真的降分，<strong>区分度就会更多依赖口语和听力</strong>，这恰恰是KET/PET一直在训练的方向。\n</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 我的判断</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">高考英语如果真降分，会让那些只会刷题、不会用英语的孩子更吃亏。真正有国际认证、听说读写均衡的孩子反而优势更明显。所以这个时候，<strong>把KET/PET认认真真备考才是正解。</strong></p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">03 现在最该做什么</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 8px\">? 备考不受政策影响的行动清单</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  ✅ 4月春季KET/PET机考正在报名，<strong>截止日期看当地考场</strong><br>\n  ✅ 词汇打基础：KET需要1500词，PET需要2500词<br>\n  ✅ 每天坚持练：听力15分钟 + 阅读一篇 + 单词打卡<br>\n  ✅ 不要因为政策风向反复就放弃备考计划\n</p>\n</section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最后说一句：<strong>孩子的英语能力是实实在在的，任何政策都带不走。</strong><br>别被每次政策讨论带着焦虑起伏，踏踏实实备考才是最稳的。</p><section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;margin:0 0 12px\">? 总结速记</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? 提案≠政策，高考英语降分还未落地</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? KET/PET是国际认证，不受高考政策影响</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? 听说能力反而变得更重要，KET/PET备考方向没错</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? 4月春季机考报名中，现在开始备考正是时候</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"background:#07c160;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;text-align:center;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 10px\">? 每日英语打卡</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0\">微信搜索 <strong>英语陪跑go</strong><br>进入「单词大乱斗」每天练10题<br>坚持21天，备考能力稳步提升 ?</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得转发给需要的家长！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpQV0KZvI2Npby82KZ-igyZ2zCcZG8pjp1HbS8JOSDjKF',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 13:03:55','2026-03-19 13:03:55',0,NULL),(63,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpc3R7c9ZhXqLznG4EDtyK1r_2nJ4k-5FQLkiNLjU_QrX','2025年后KET/PET悄悄变了——新题型你知道吗？','英语陪跑go','KET词汇量增加到1500个，PET新增100词写作，听力口音更多样。还按旧版备考可能会踩坑！','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「KET资料」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">很多家长不知道一件事：<strong>2025年起，KET和PET考试悄悄变了。</strong><br><br>不是小变——词汇量增加了，阅读难了，PET写作有新题型，听力口音也更多样了。<br><br>如果还按照旧版备考，可能会在考场上遇到\"怎么和练习册不一样\"的情况。今天帮你把变化说清楚。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">01 KET的变化</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  <strong>① 词汇量要求提高</strong><br>\n  旧版：约1200个 → 新版：约1500个<br>\n  增加了更多\"真实生活场景\"词汇，比如数字设备、社交媒体相关词<br><br>\n  <strong>② 阅读难度提升</strong><br>\n  文章更长，话题更贴近真实生活，不再是简单的单句题<br><br>\n  <strong>③ 写作新增\"便条/短信\"题型</strong><br>\n  要求用25-35个词写一条短信或便条，更考验实际表达\n</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 备考重点</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">新版KET更强调\"用英语做事\"，不是死背单词就行。建议用真实场景对话来练习，比如用英语给朋友发消息、写购物清单等。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">02 PET的变化</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  <strong>① 写作要求提高</strong><br>\n  新增\"文章写作\"题型，需要写100个词左右的完整文章<br>\n  不再只是填句子，要有逻辑结构：开头-中间-结尾<br><br>\n  <strong>② 听力场景更广</strong><br>\n  加入了播客、广播采访等更真实的听力材料<br>\n  口音更多样，不只是英式英语，美式、澳式都有<br><br>\n  <strong>③ 口语互动升级</strong><br>\n  考官会引导更自然的对话，不再是固定问题固定回答\n</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 备考重点</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">PET写作是很多考生的弱项，建议现在就开始练习\"100词文章\"：选一个话题，写3段，第一段说是什么，第二段说为什么，第三段给结论。每周练2篇，考前就不慌了。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">03 用哪些资料备考新版</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 8px\">? 推荐备考材料</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  ✅ <strong>剑桥官方新版真题册</strong>（2023年后出版的，注意看版本）<br>\n  ✅ <strong>剑桥官网免费题库</strong>：cambridgeenglish.org，有免费练习题<br>\n  ✅ <strong>词汇APP</strong>：扇贝、不背单词，选\"KET词汇\"专题<br>\n  ✅ <strong>每日打卡</strong>：回复「KET资料」或「PET资料」获取本号整理的词汇清单\n</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;margin:0 0 12px\">? 总结速记</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">KET新版：词汇1500个，阅读更长，写作加便条题型</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">PET新版：写作100词文章，听力口音更多样，口语更自然</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">⚠️ 一定用2023年后出版的官方真题，旧版有差异</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? 现在开始备考，4月机考时间足够充裕</p>\n</section>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"background:#07c160;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;text-align:center;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 10px\">? 每日英语打卡</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0\">微信搜索 <strong>英语陪跑go</strong><br>进入「单词大乱斗」每天练10题<br>坚持21天，备考能力稳步提升 ?</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得转发给需要的家长！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpbyhuRoJJiEZgYKPv5riXApjX6Li-qTdee5mfiM0belA',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 13:04:00','2026-03-19 13:04:00',0,NULL),(64,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0Qacwpd114BNqbaTzGSu7Q-dOIO5zfpjgALQc3er1BoTsSIfq','老外讲完这5个笑话，全班中国人都没笑——看完你懂了','英语陪跑go','英语谐音梗第二弹！No eye deer / Lost interest / Put down / Make up everything，全是真实在用的，听懂了算入门。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「英语谐音」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">上次发了5个英语谐音梗，好多人留言说听懂了，还有人说讲给外教听，外教笑了半天。<br><br>今天继续，再来5个——这次难度稍微升级一点，有造词双关，有一词多义，有谐音绕口，<strong>全部都是老外社交场合真实在用的</strong>，听懂了你就算入门了。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">1. What do you call a deer with no eyes?</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❓ 问：</strong>What do you call a deer with no eyes?（没有眼睛的鹿叫什么？）</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e05c00;font-weight:bold;margin:0\"><strong>? 答：</strong>No eye deer!</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 笑点在哪？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>no eye deer</strong> 听起来和 <strong>no idea（不知道）</strong>几乎一模一样！<br><br>老外问这句话，其实是在考你：你是回答\"不知道\"，还是 get 到了这是个谐音梗？<br>知道这个梗之后，下次有人问你，你可以装作认真地说\"Hmm, no idea…\"，然后看对方的反应。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">2. I used to be a banker, but I lost interest.</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❓ 问：</strong>Why did the banker quit his job?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e05c00;font-weight:bold;margin:0\"><strong>? 答：</strong>Because he lost interest.</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 笑点在哪？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>interest</strong> 有两个意思：<br>① <strong>兴趣</strong>（lost interest = 失去兴趣）<br>② <strong>利息</strong>（银行的 interest = 利息）<br><br>银行家不干了，因为\"失去了兴趣\"，同时也暗示\"没有了利息\"——银行人听到这个笑话会很有共鸣。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">3. I\'m reading a book about anti-gravity.</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❓ 问：</strong>I\'m reading a book about anti-gravity. What do you think?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e05c00;font-weight:bold;margin:0\"><strong>? 答：</strong>It\'s impossible to put down!</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 笑点在哪？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>put down</strong> 有两个意思：<br>① <strong>放下（书）</strong> → 好看的书让人放不下<br>② <strong>放下（物体）</strong> → 反重力让东西无法放下<br><br>表面是夸书好看，实际是说反重力的书物理上就放不下——双关完美。这种\"表面说一件事，实际说另一件事\"的梗是英语幽默的精髓。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">4. Why don\'t scientists trust atoms?</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❓ 问：</strong>Why don\'t scientists trust atoms?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e05c00;font-weight:bold;margin:0\"><strong>? 答：</strong>Because they make up everything!</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 笑点在哪？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>make up</strong> 有两个意思：<br>① <strong>组成、构成</strong>（原子构成万物）<br>② <strong>编造、瞎说</strong>（make up stories = 编故事）<br><br>原子构成了一切，所以科学家\"不信任\"原子——因为它们\"构成/编造了一切\"。理科生听到这个笑话会立刻笑出来。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">5. What do you call a fish without eyes?</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;margin:0 0 8px\"><strong>❓ 问：</strong>What do you call a fish without eyes?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e05c00;font-weight:bold;margin:0\"><strong>? 答：</strong>A fsh!</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 笑点在哪？</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">这个是纯视觉梗：<strong>fish 去掉 i（眼睛）= fsh</strong><br><br>英语里 i 和\"eye\"谐音，没有眼睛（no i）的 fish 就变成了 fsh。<br>这类文字游戏在英语里叫 wordplay，比谐音更进一步，需要你看到字母层面的联系。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;margin:0 0 12px\">? 总结速记</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? No eye deer = No idea（不知道）</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? Lost interest = 失去兴趣 / 没有利息</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? Impossible to put down = 好看 / 反重力放不下</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">⚛️ Make up everything = 构成万物 / 编造一切</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? Fish - i = fsh（没有眼睛的鱼）</p>\n</section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">英语幽默的核心其实就一件事：<strong>一个词或句子，同时成立两个意思。</strong><br><br>听懂了这5个，你的英语语感已经比大多数人强了。下次老外说完笑话，跟着笑就对了。</p>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"background:#07c160;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;text-align:center;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 10px\">? 每日英语打卡</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0\">微信搜索 <strong>英语陪跑go</strong><br>进入「单词大乱斗」每天练10题<br>坚持21天，备考能力稳步提升 ?</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得转发给需要的家长！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpSdBdsdKIUc2HeVWr6JuFPJbEE2wY7V7nYwqW03nqTwu',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 13:04:05','2026-03-19 13:04:05',0,NULL),(65,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpTTBJgRN44eIokQpNjz8NXhCh6d1GUe4F7e-cezjbnrN','孩子说了这5句话，说明英语基础有漏洞（越早发现越好）','英语陪跑go','周末在培训机构等孩子，总结了5个信号——孩子有1-2个说明局部需补，有3个以上建议系统梳理。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「备考指南」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">周末在培训机构等孩子下课，旁边家长聊到孩子英语成绩还不错，但每次写作文都\"差那么一口气\"。<br><br>我听完问了一句：<strong>\"孩子平时说英语，有没有这几句话？\"</strong><br><br>如果有，说明某一块基础没打牢，现在补还来得及。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">信号1 总说\"Yes, yes, yes\"表示理解</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>表现：</strong>听完对方说话，只会说\"Yes, yes\"或者\"OK, OK\"<br><strong>漏洞：</strong>回应词汇量不足，不知道怎么用英语表达\"我明白了/有道理/确实\"</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 练习方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">学几个真实回应词：<br>\nI see. / That makes sense. / Exactly! / Right! / Got it.<br>\n每个场景选一个，练到张口就来，回应自然了口语就活了。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">信号2 时态全部用现在时</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>表现：</strong>\"Yesterday I go to school.\" / \"Last week I eat pizza.\"<br><strong>漏洞：</strong>时态概念没有内化，说话时不自动切换过去时</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 练习方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">每天写3句\"昨天发生的事\"，强制用过去时。不用很长，\"I woke up at 7. I ate breakfast. I went to school.\" 坚持2周，过去时就会变成本能。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">信号3 描述东西只会用\"very + 形容词\"</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>表现：</strong>everything is \"very good\", \"very nice\", \"very big\"<br><strong>漏洞：</strong>形容词词汇量少，表达层次单一，作文分数上不去</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 练习方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">用\"升级替换\"法：<br>very good → excellent / wonderful / fantastic<br>very big → huge / enormous / massive<br>very tired → exhausted<br>每天替换3个词，1个月后作文用词会明显丰富。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">信号4 问问题全靠语调不靠语法</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>表现：</strong>\"You go to school tomorrow?\" （靠语调表示疑问，没有倒装）<br><strong>漏洞：</strong>疑问句结构没有掌握，在笔试中会直接失分</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 练习方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">疑问句三步口诀：<strong>助动词提前 → 主语 → 动词原形</strong><br>You go → Do you go?<br>She can come → Can she come?<br>每天造5个疑问句，考试时自然就对了。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">信号5 连接词只有\"and\"和\"but\"</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.85;margin:0\"><strong>表现：</strong>所有句子都是\"... and ... but ... and ...\"<br><strong>漏洞：</strong>逻辑连接词贫乏，PET作文分数直接受影响</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">✅ 练习方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">学会这6个就够用：<br>however（然而）/ therefore（因此）/ in addition（另外）/ although（虽然）/ as a result（结果是）/ for example（例如）<br>每次写作文，强制用其中3个，用熟了就是加分项。</p>\n</section><section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;margin:0 0 12px\">? 总结速记</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">信号1：只会说Yes → 补充回应词汇</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">信号2：时态全用现在时 → 每天写3句过去时</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">信号3：全是very+形容词 → 做\"升级替换\"练习</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">信号4：靠语调问问题 → 练疑问句倒装结构</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">信号5：只用and和but → 学会6个逻辑连接词</p>\n</section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">这5个信号，如果孩子有1-2个，说明局部需要补；如果有3个以上，说明基础层面需要系统梳理了。<br><br>越早发现，越容易纠正。</p>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"background:#07c160;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;text-align:center;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 10px\">? 每日英语打卡</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0\">微信搜索 <strong>英语陪跑go</strong><br>进入「单词大乱斗」每天练10题<br>坚持21天，备考能力稳步提升 ?</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得转发给需要的家长！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpZk8_ch-WtaCDqrHwTxnRJvpAhOfOsYn3qCuAhSNe7yZ',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 13:04:10','2026-03-19 13:04:10',0,NULL),(66,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpZt3Uy4paerOMDuu8CCVRIlDovXHSEDIopDdilt1oISV','春季KET/PET机考还有3-4周，这份冲刺计划直接用','英语陪跑go','4月报名截止，现在开始不晚。4周冲刺计划：摸底→攻弱项→模拟→调状态，每周做什么说清楚。','<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 24px\"><p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px\">✨ 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p></section>\n<section style=\"background:#4a90e2;padding:20px 18px;border-radius:10px;margin:24px 0;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 粉丝福利</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;margin:0\">关注公众号，回复<strong>「PET资料」</strong>获取本文 PDF + 更多备考资料</p>\n</section>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">春季KET/PET机考，大多数考场的报名截止在4月初。<br><br>从现在算，<strong>还有大约3-4周准备时间。</strong><br><br>这段时间怎么用，决定了孩子进考场时是\"心里有底\"还是\"能过就过\"。今天给一个实操的冲刺计划，不废话，直接用。</p><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第1周 摸底 + 找准弱项</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  ? <strong>做一套完整真题</strong>（模拟考场环境，限时）<br>\n  ? <strong>统计错误分布：</strong>听力错几道？阅读错几道？写作扣几分？<br>\n  ? <strong>找出最弱的一项，第2-3周重点攻它</strong><br><br>\n  ⚠️ 不要一上来就全面复习，时间不够用。找准弱项，集中打击效率最高。\n</p></section><section style=\"background:#fffbe6;border-left:4px solid #f39c12;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:12px 0 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#d68910;margin:0 0 6px\">? 测试建议</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:1.85;margin:0\">用官方真题而不是模拟题，剑桥官网有免费样题，格式和真实考试完全一样。</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第2-3周 针对弱项强化</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 8px\">? 听力弱 → 这样练</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  每天精听20分钟：听一遍，记关键词，再听一遍验证<br>\n  重点练\"数字、时间、地点\"这类考试高频场景<br>\n  推荐材料：BBC Learning English / 剑桥真题音频\n</p>\n</section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 8px\">? 阅读弱 → 这样练</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  练\"带问题读\"：先看题目，再读文章，定位答案<br>\n  不要逐字读，找关键词，答案一般在段落开头或结尾<br>\n  每天做1篇阅读题，不用很长，保持手感\n</p>\n</section><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f8f0;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #27ae60\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin:0 0 8px\">? 写作弱 → 这样练</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  KET：练25-35词的短便条，每天1篇，格式固定<br>\n  PET：练100词文章，三段式：引出话题→具体说明→总结<br>\n  写完对照评分标准，看有没有漏掉要求的信息点\n</p>\n</section><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\"><h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;border-left:4px solid #3498db;padding-left:12px;margin:24px 0 15px\">第4周（考前7天） 模拟 + 调整状态</h2><section style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:15px 16px;background:#e8f4fd;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #4a90e2\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:2;margin:0\">\n  ? 再做一套完整真题，和第1周对比提升了多少<br>\n  ? <strong>不要再学新知识了，复习已掌握的内容</strong><br>\n  ? 确认考场地点、考试时间、需要带的证件<br>\n  ? 考前一天早点睡，状态比突击重要<br><br>\n  ✅ <strong>考前注意：</strong>听力部分开始前有时间看题目，先把题目浏览一遍，听的时候直接找答案。\n</p></section><section style=\"background:#ffe5b4;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;border-left:4px solid #f5a623\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;color:#f5a623;margin:0 0 12px\">? 总结速记</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">第1周：做真题，找最弱的一项</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">第2-3周：集中攻弱项，每天30分钟定向练习</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">第4周：模拟考，不学新知识，调整状态</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? 确认报名截止日期，别错过</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#5d4037;line-height:2;margin:0\">? 稳住心态，发挥平时水平就是胜利</p>\n</section><p style=\"line-height:1.85;font-size:16px;color:#333;margin:15px 0\">最后说一点：<strong>KET/PET不是\"难\"，是\"陌生\"。</strong><br><br>考试内容其实很固定，题型不变，场景不变，考点不变。练熟了，进考场就是\"我见过这个\"，不会慌。<br><br>现在开始，时间够用。</p>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:2px dashed #e0e0e0;margin:30px 0\">\n<section style=\"background:#07c160;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:30px 0;text-align:center;color:#fff\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 10px\">? 每日英语打卡</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0\">微信搜索 <strong>英语陪跑go</strong><br>进入「单词大乱斗」每天练10题<br>坚持21天，备考能力稳步提升 ?</p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"text-align:center;margin:20px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 8px\">? 觉得有用，记得转发给需要的家长！</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#3a3a3a;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px\">? 评论区打卡，坚持21天送备考资料</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:25px 0 15px\">— THE END —</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0\">英语陪跑 go · 每日英语干货</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#6a6a6a;font-size:13px;margin:4px 0\">关注我，KET/PET 不迷路</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#999;font-size:12px;margin:15px 0 5px\">? 原创内容 · 禁止转载</p>\n</section>',NULL,'-pWAWR_jDt42Uvr0QacwpcD5pVz8Ru7wQxFm72kx4XJWHg7BlZr_O5XbdowtYCPJ',NULL,1,0,0,'auto',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,0,0,'2026-03-19 13:04:14','2026-03-19 13:04:14',0,NULL);
